ooting-updates-rpf-constable-who-killed-4-on-train-to-be-charged-with-promoting-enmity-sources-4275924%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rocky%20Aur%20Rani%20Kii%20Prem%20Kahaani%20%20Makes%20Its%20100%20Crore%20(More%20Than%2C%20In%20Fact)%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EKaran%20Johar's%20%3Cem%3ERocky%20Aur%20Rani%20Kii%20Prem%20Kahaani%3C%2Fem%3E%20made%20its%20Rs%20100%20crore%20over%20the%20weekend%2C%20with%20a%20second%20Sunday%20collection%20of%20Rs%2013.50%20crore%2C%20reports%20trade%20analyst%20Taran%20Adarsh.%20The%20film's%20total%20earnings%20so%20far%20is%20Rs%20105.08%20crore.%20The%20second%20Saturday-Sunday%20business%20proves%20that%20ordinary%20weekends%20have%20box%20office%20potential%2C%20Mr%20Adarsh%20commented%2C%20adding%20that%20%3Cem%3ERocky%20Aur%20Rani%3C%2Fem%3E's%20numbers%20should%20also%20silence%20critics%20who%20underestimated%20the%20film%20based%20on%20its%20%26quot%3Bmoderate%26quot%3B%20opening%20day%20earnings.%20%3Cem%3ERocky%20Aur%20Rani%20Kii%20Prem%20Kahaani%3C%2Fem%3E%20released%20on%20July%2028.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20film%20is%20this%20year's%20sixth%20Bollywood%20offering%20to%20have%20hit%20a%20century.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%3Cem%3ERocky%20Aur%20Rani%20Prem%20Kahaani%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20100%20not%20out.%20Packs%20a%20solid%20score%20in%20Weekend%202%20(Rs%2031.75%20crore).%20The%20jump%20on%20second%20Saturday-Sunday%20should%20silence%20all%20naysayers%20who%20wrote%20off%20the%20film%20after%20its%20moderate%20Day%201.%20(Week%202)%20Friday%206.75%20crore%2C%20Saturday%2011.50%20crore%2C%20Sunday%2013.50%20crore.%20Total%3A%20Rs%20105.08%20crore.%20India%20biz%2C%26quot%3B%20Taran%20Adarsh%20tweeted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20jump%20on%20(second)%20Saturday-Sunday%20is%20an%20eye%20opener%20for%20those%20who%20feel%20only%20national%20holidays%2Ffestivals%20yield%20best%20results%20at%20the%20box%20office.%20Let's%20face%20it%2C%20even%20an%20ordinary%20weekend%20can%20fetch%20impressive%20nu