ot%3BConfidence%20Building%20means%20buildings%2C%20homes%20and%20medical%20shops%20and%20shanties%20of%20one%20community%20(Muslims)%20should%20be%20Demolished%20without%20following%20due%20process%20to%20give%20collective%20punishment.%20The%20%40mlkhattar%20government%20has%20usurped%20the%20rights%20of%20Courts%20of%20Law%20Confidence%20is%20being%20given%20to%20people%20who%20are%20ideologically%20closer%20to%20BJP%2FSangh%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20district%20administration%20also%20drew%20fire%20after%20they%20stopped%20a%20four-member%20delegation%20from%20CPI%20from%20entering%20Nuh%20district.%20The%20argument%20between%20the%20CPI%20leaders%20and%20the%20police%20was%20caught%20on%20camera.%20CPI%20MP%20Binoy%20Viswam%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20plight%20of%20the%20country%20today.%20The%20reality%20of%20the%20day%2C%20the%20Police%20are%20not%20allowing%20even%20us.%20That%20means%20that%20under%20this%20rule%2C%20even%20the%20freedom%20of%20movement%20is%20prohibited.%20Hooligans%2C%20goons%20and%20fascists%20can%20move%20freely%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETension%20continues%20to%20grip%20the%20areas%20affected%20by%20the%20communal%20violence.%20Many%20of%20these%20areas%20are%20under%20curfew%20and%20paramilitary%20forces%20are%20on%20the%20ground%20to%20prevent%20any%20flare-up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20curfew%20was%20relaxed%20for%20four%20hours%20this%20morning%2C%20during%20which%20ATMs%20were%20also%20opened.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Internet%20ban%20in%20the%20area%20continues%20to%20remain%20in%20force.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20150%20people%20have%20been%20arrested%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20clashes%20and%2056%20cases%20registered%2C%20Nuh%20police%20have%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691393640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fenogdqb8_nuh-sahara-hotel-bulldozer_625x300_06_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22