s%2Fnew-grads-have-no-idea-how-to-behave-in-the-office-help-is-on-the-way-677f6ba1%3Fmod%3Dhp_listc_pos3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Wall%20Street%20Journal.%3C%2Fa%3E%20The%20courses%2C%20which%20cover%20how%20to%20behave%20in%20an%20office%2C%20what%20to%20wear%2C%20and%20other%20necessary%20soft%20skills%2C%20may%20prove%20beneficial%20%E2%80%94%20they're%20the%20%26quot%3Betiquette%20classes%26quot%3B%20many%20of%20the%20business%20leaders%20surveyed%20by%20Intelligent%20suggested%20could%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmanagers-avoid-hiring-recent-gen-z-college-graduates-unprepared-survey-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691393521000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64cd2f988df5080019d31253%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmanagers-avoid-hiring-recent-gen-z-college-graduates-unprepared-survey-2023-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%2240%25%20of%20business%20leaders%20in%20a%20new%20survey%20indicated%20recent%20Gen%20Z%20college%20grads%20are%20unprepared%20for%20the%20workplace.%20Some%20recommended%20%26quot%3Betiquette%20classes.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22htenore%40insider.com%20(Haley%20Tenore)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A30%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmanagers-avoid-hiring-recent-gen-z-college-graduates-unprepared-survey-2023-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Parliamentary%20Panel%20Cautions%20EC%20Against%20Rushing%20to%20Prepare%20Common%20Electoral%20Roll%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2F10111348%2FEC.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20Parliamentary%20Standing%20Committee%20has%20cautioned%20the%20Election%20Commission%20(EC)%20against%20rushing%20to%20prepare%20a%20common%20electoral%20roll%20without%20looking%20into%20the%20Constitutional%20provisions%20and%20powers%20of%20states%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EDeccan%20Herald%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Felections%2Findia%2Felection-commission-should-keep-in-mind-principles-of-federalism-says-parliamentary-standing-committee-2636872%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Committee%20also%20suggested%20that%20the%20EC%20should%20adhere%20to%20principles%20of%20%E2%80%9Cfederalism%20enshrined%20in%20the%20Constitution%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Ccarefully%20assess%20potential%20consequences%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20present%2C%20the%20EC%20prepares%20the%20voter%E2%80%99s%20list%20for%20Parliament%20and%20Assembly%20polls%20while%20for%20local%20body%20polls%2C%20the%20electoral%20roll%20is%20prepared%20by%20the%20State%20Election%20Commission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Committee%20suggested%20that%20the%20EC%20should%20hold%20extensive%20consultations%20with%20the%20central%20government%E2%80%99s%20law%20department%2C%20state%20governments%20and%20parties%20while%20expressing%20concerns%20about%20the%20potential%20impact%20of%20a%20common%20roll%20on%20the%20constitutional%20powers%20of%20the%20states%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EDeccan%20Herald%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20ECI%20may%20also%20keep%20in%20mind%20the%20principles%20of%20federalism%20enshrined%20under%20the%20constitution%20and%20the%20powers%20reserved%20for%20the%20State%20Election%20Commissions%20under%20List%20II%20Entry%205%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20%E2%80%98Specific%20Aspects%20of%20Election%20Process%20and%20Their%20Reform%E2%80%99%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20is%20in%20favour%20of%20a%20common%20electoral%20roll%20%E2%80%93%20a%20suggestion%20which%20was%20first%20made%20in%201999%20by%20the%20then%20chief%20election%20commissioner%20through%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20prime%20minister%20%E2%80%93%20as%20it%20believes%20it%20would%20reduce%20the%20cost%20and%20efforts%20involved%20in%20the%20process%20of%20preparing%20separate%20lists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20said%20the%20committee%20has%20taken%20note%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Cpotential%20benefits%E2%80%9D%20of%20a%20common%20electoral%20roll%20but%20it%20stressed%20the%20importance%20of%20proper%20constitutional%20and%20statutory%20authorisation%20before%20the%20EC%20takes%20charge%20of%20creating%20electoral%20rolls%20for%20State%20Election%20Commissions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20committee%20also%20cautioned%20the%20EC%20against%20treating%20all%20regions%20in%20India%20as%20identical%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20panel%20further%20observed%20that%20implementing%20the%20common%20roll%20is%20currently%20outside%20the%20scope%20of%20Article%20325%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20%3Cem%3EThePrint%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Findia%2Fgovernance%2Fhouse-panel-cautions-modi-govt-on-proposed-common-voter-list-avoid-stepping-into-states-domain%2F1700380%2F%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20Article%20stipulates%20that%20separate%20electoral%20rolls%20must%20be%20used%20for%20elections%20to%20Parliament%20and%20the%20state%20legislatures.%20The%20panel%20suggested%20that%20to%20ensure%20that%20all%20actions%20are%20in%20line%20with%20the%20Constitution%2C%20%E2%80%9Cconsensus%20shall%20be%20made%20in%20line%20with%20Article%20325%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBy%20conducting%20these%20consultations%2C%20a%20final%20proposal%20on%20a%20Common%20Electoral%20Roll%20can%20be%20developed%20taking%20into%20consideration%20the%20different%20viewpoints%20and%20concerns%20of%20all%20parties%20involved%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20panel%20said%20in%20its%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691393447000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2F10111348%2FEC.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fparliamentary-panel-cautions-ec-against-rushing-to-prepare-common-electoral-roll%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20panel%20suggested%20that%20the%20EC%20should%20adhere%20to%20principles%20of%20%E2%80%9Cfederalism%20enshrined%20in%20the%20Constitution%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Ccarefully%20assess%20potential%20consequences%E2%80%9D.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fparliamentary-panel-cautions-ec-against-rushing-to-prepare-common-electoral-roll%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Video%3A%20Chhattisgarh%20Chief%20Minister's%20'Balancing%20Act'%20On%20Stilts%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691393340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F3s4upb0o_bhupesh-baghel_640x480_07_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fvideo%2Fnews%2Fnews%2Fvideo-chhattisgarh-chief-minister-s-balancing-act-on-stilts-716092%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fvideo%2Fnews%2Fnews%2Fvideo-chhattisgarh-chief-minister-s-balancing-act-on-stilts-716092%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20Approves%20First%20Pill%20For%20Postpartum%20Depression%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20has%20approved%20the%20first%20pill%20for%20postpartum%20depression.%20As%20per%20a%20report%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-66414446%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EBBC%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20US%20Food%20and%20Drug%20Administration%20(FDA)%20on%20Friday%20approved%20for%20the%20first%20time%20a%20pill%20to%20treat%20postpartum%20depression%2C%20a%20condition%20believed%20to%20affect%20around%20half%20a%20million%20women%20in%20the%20country%20every%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20FDA%20said%20zuranolone%20is%20%26quot%3Bthe%20first%20oral%20medication%20indicated%20to%20treat%20postpartum%20depression%20(PPD)%20in%20adults.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUntil%20now%2C%20treatment%20for%20PPD%20was%20only%20available%20as%20an%20IV%20injection%20given%20by%20a%20health%20care%20provider%20in%20certain%20health%20care%20facilities%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESymptoms%20of%20postpartum%20depression%20can%20include%20sadness%2C%20loss%20of%20energy%2C%20suicidal%20thoughts%2C%20decreased%20ability%20to%20feel%20pleasure%2C%20or%20cognitive%20impairment%2C%20as%20per%20the%20FDA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Asima%20Ahmad%2C%20the%20chief%20medical%20officer%20at%20Carrot%20Fertility%2C%20a%20healthcare%20company%20in%20Menlo%20Park%2C%20California%2C%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Babout%20one%20in%20eight%20women%20experience%20PPD%20symptoms%20after%20a%20recent%20live%20birth%2C%20and%20among%20those%20reporting%20symptoms%2C%2075%20per%20cent%20go%20untreated.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20numbers%20are%20elevated%20for%20minority%20populations%3B%2081%20per%20cent%20of%20Black%20women%20and%2076%20per%20cent%20of%20Hispanic%20women%20said%20they%20would%20have%20liked%20to%20learn%20more%20about%20postpartum%20mental%20health%20before%20having%20children%2C%20compared%20to%2070%20per%20cent%20of%20women%20overall%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20time%20when%20we%20are%20seeing%20rising%20maternal%20mortality%20rates%20and%20significant%20racial%20disparities%20in%20maternal%20outcomes%2C%20we%20need%20to%20focus%20on%20solutions%2C%20and%20that%20includes%20addressing%20postpartum%20depression.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20pill%2C%20specifically%20designed%20for%20postpartum%20depression%2C%20has%20been%20shown%20to%20work%20faster%20than%20other%20antidepressants%20and%20is%20designed%20to%20be%20taken%20only%20over%20a%20short%20two-week%20period%2C%20as%20per%20%3Cem%3EAFP%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20doctor%20said%20that%20the%20side%20effects%20of%20the%20pill%20were%20less%20severe%20than%20other%20antidepressants%20currently%20in%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBoth%20the%20lower%20incidence%20of%20side%20effects%20and%20the%20short-term%20regimen%2C%20which%20could%20help%20some%20feel%20less%20stigma%20around%20having%20to%20use%20an%20antidepressant%2C%20could%20potentially%20improve%20compliance%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETiffany%20Farchione%2C%20head%20of%20psychiatry%20in%20the%20FDA's%20Center%20for%20Drug%20Evaluation%20and%20Research%2C%20said%20postpartum%20depression%20is%20%26quot%3Ba%20serious%20and%20potentially%20life-threatening%20condition%20in%20which%20women%20experience%20sadness%2C%20guilt%2C%20worthlessness%20--%20even%2C%20in%20severe%20cases%2C%20thoughts%20of%20harming%20themselves%20or%20their%20child.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHaving%20access%20to%20an%20oral%20medication%20will%20be%20a%20beneficial%20option%20for%20many%20of%20these%20women%20coping%20with%20extreme%2C%20and%20sometimes%20life-threatening%2C%20feelings%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20pill%20will%20be%20marketed%20under%20the%20brand%20name%20Zurzuvae%20and%20was%20developed%20by%20Massachusetts-based%20Sage%20Therapeutics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F08%2F04%2Fhealth%2Fpostpartum-depression-pill-fda.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ENew%20York%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20only%20other%20drug%20approved%20for%20postpartum%20depression%20is%20brexanolone%2C%20which%20was%20approved%20by%20the%20FDA%20in%202019%20but%20requires%20a%2060-hour%20intravenous%20infusion%20in%20a%20hospital%2C%20and%20costs%20%2434%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20price%20has%20yet%20been%20announced%20for%20the%20new%20oral%20pill.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691392860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2021-09%2F66j8a