ome%20generated%20from%20the%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20legal%20notice%20also%20said%20that%20on%20the%20one%20hand%2C%20the%20couple%20were%20introduced%20as%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20real%20heroes%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20elite%2C%20celebrities%2C%20sports%20persons%20and%20political%20leaders%2C%20gaining%20wide%20publicity%20for%20them.%20But%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20filmmaker%20got%20all%20the%20financial%20benefits%20from%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20India%2C%20the%20notice%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20PTI%20reached%20out%20to%20Bomman%2C%20he%20said%20he%20was%20advised%20not%20to%20talk%20about%20the%20case%20anymore%20and%20asked%20us%20to%20get%20in%20touch%20with%20his%20lawyers%20for%20further%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChennai-based%20social%20activist%20Pravin%20Raj%2C%20a%20lawyer%20by%20profession%2C%20who%20said%20he%20has%20known%20the%20couple%20for%20almost%20a%20decade%2C%20said%20he%20put%20them%20in%20touch%20with%20a%20law%20firm%20in%20Chennai%20when%20the%20couple%20approached%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBoth%20Bomman%20and%20Bellie%20are%20disappointed%20with%20Gonsalves%2C%20who%20had%20promised%20them%20monetary%20help%20as%20well%20as%20help%20with%20the%20education%20of%20Bellie's%20granddaughter%2C%20while%20making%20the%20film.%20But%20she%20now%20refuses%20to%20give%20even%20a%20fraction%20of%20the%20enormous%20profits%20made%20by%20the%20film%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Raj.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20couple%20have%20been%20following%20the%20documentary%20maker%20around%2C%20doing%20what%20she%20was%20asking%20them%20to%20do%2C%20in%20the%20hope%20that%20when%20the%20film%20did%20well%2C%20they%20would%20all%20prosper%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CInstead%2C%20Gonsalves%20is%20not%20even%20picking%20up%20the%20phone%20when%20Bomman%20calls%2C%E2%80%9D%20added%20Raj.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdvocate%20Mohammed%20Mansoor%20who%20is%20handling%20the%20case%20said%20four%20days%20ago%20he%20received%20a%20reply%20notice%20from%20Sikhya%20Entertainment%20Pvt%20Ltd%2C%20on%20behalf%20of%20Gonsalves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20that%2C%20she%20has%20flatly%20refused%20any%20more%20help%20stating%20that%20she%20has%20already%20given%20money%20to%20the%20couple.%20I%20will%20be%20sending%20her%20a%20rejoinder%20in%20a%20couple%20of%20days%20after%20consulting%20with%20my%20clients%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Mansoor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20in%20a%20statement%20issued%20by%20Sikhya%20Entertainment%20Pvt%20Ltd%20to%20the%20PTI%2C%20it%20is%20stated%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20goal%20in%20creating%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Elephant%20Whisperers%20%3C%2Fem%3Ehas%20always%20been%20to%20highlight%20elephant%20conservation%2C%20the%20tremendous%20efforts%20of%20the%20forest%20department%20and%20its%20mahouts%20Bomman%20and%20Bellie.%20Since%20its%20launch%2C%20the%20documentary%20has%20raised%20awareness%20of%20the%20cause%20and%20had%20a%20real%20impact%20on%20the%20mahouts%20and%20cavadis%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChief%20minister%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%20M%20K%20Stalin%20has%20made%20donations%20towards%20assisting%20the%2091%20mahouts%20and%20cavadis%20who%20look%20after%20the%20state's%20elephants%2C%20constructing%20eco-friendly%20houses%20for%20the%20caretakers%20and%20developing%20an%20elephant%20camp%20in%20the%20Anamalai%20Tiger%20Reserve.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20documentary%20has%20been%20celebrated%20by%20heads%20of%20state%20across%20India%2C%20and%20the%20Academy%20Award%20is%20a%20moment%20of%20national%20pride%20that%20has%20brought%20widespread%20recognition%20for%20the%20work%20of%20mahouts%20like%20Bomman%20and%20Bellie.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20claims%20made%20are%20untrue.%20We%20have%20deep%20respect%20for%20all%20of%20the%20contributors%20of%20this%20story%2C%20and%20remain%20driven%20by%20the%20desire%20to%20create%20positive%20change.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3C