F2023%2Ffilm%2Fglobal%2Fnelson-yeo-momo-film-co-1235689002%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ffilm%2Fglobal%2Fnelson-yeo-momo-film-co-1235689002%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Is%20WFH%20Better%20Or%20In-Office%3F%20On%20Raging%20Boardroom%20Debate%2C%20New%20Study%20Says%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20heated%20debate%20over%20the%20value%20of%20remote%20versus%20in-office%20work%20has%20found%20fresh%20ammunition%20with%20new%20research%20revealing%20lower%20productivity%20when%20working%20from%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20study%20by%20economists%20at%20the%20Massachusetts%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20and%20the%20University%20of%20California%2C%20Los%20Angeles%20found%20that%20workers%20randomly%20assigned%20to%20work%20from%20home%20full-time%20are%2018%25%20less%20productive%20than%20those%20in%20the%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20researchers%2C%20who%20studied%20newly%20hired%20data%20entry%20workers%20in%20India%20who%20were%20randomly%20assigned%20to%20either%20the%20home%20or%20the%20office%2C%20said%20that%20two-thirds%20of%20the%20drop%20in%20productivity%20was%20evident%20from%20the%20first%20day%20of%20work.%20The%20remaining%20difference%20showed%20up%20over%20time%20as%20in-office%20workers%20learned%20more%20quickly%20than%20their%20fully%20remote%20counterparts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESurprisingly%2C%20remote%20workers%20who%20preferred%20to%20work%20from%20home%20were%20even%20less%20productive%20than%20those%20who%20would%20rather%20have%20been%20in%20the%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20authors%20said%20their%20findings%20aren't%20prescriptive%2C%20the%20paper%20marks%20the%20latest%20salvo%20in%20a%20debate%20that's%20raged%20inside%20boardrooms%2C%20Slack%20chats%20and%20academic%20circles%20ever%20since%20the%20pandemic%20forced%20work-from-home%20into%20the%20mainstream.%20The%20warring%20camps%20can%20now%20each%20cite%20research%20that%20supports%20their%20views%2C%20whether%20they%20subscribe%20to%20JPMorgan%20Chase%20%26amp%3B%20Co.%20Chief%20Executive%20Officer%20Jamie%20Dimon's%20view%20that%20remote%20work%20%26quot%3Bdoesn't%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20or%20Airbnb%20Inc.%20CEO%20Brian%20Chesky's%20pro-flexibility%20stance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Jose%20Maria%20Barrero%2C%20an%20economist%20and%20co-founder%20of%20WFH%20Research%2C%20a%20group%20dedicated%20to%20the%20study%20of%20remote%20work%20arrangements%2C%20this%20latest%20paper%20is%20consistent%20with%20others%20that%20have%20found%20fully%20remote%20work%20is%20less%20productive%20than%20fully%20in-person%20or%C2%A0%20hybrid%20work.%20Still%2C%20even%20if%20fully%20remote%20work%20is%20less%20productive%2C%20he%20notes%20it%20could%20be%20worth%20it%20for%20companies%20that%20save%20substantial%20sums%20on%20real%20estate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20research%20underscores%20the%20challenges%20inherent%20in%20productivity%20research.%20Since%20the%20workers%20in%20the%20trial%20were%20newly%20hired%2C%20their%20outcomes%20may%20differ%20from%20employees%20who%20switch%20to%20fully%20remote%20only%20after%20first%20spending%20significant%20time%20on-site.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20obviously%20going%20to%20be%20a%20big%20difference%20between%20someone%20who%20already%20understands%20the%20work%20well%20and%20already%20knows%20the%20culture%20of%20the%20firm%20and%20how%20things%20are%20done%2C%20and%20now%20you're%20saying%20'Ok%2C%20now%20you%20can%20work%20from%20home%20a%20few%20days%20a%20week%2C'%26quot%3B%20said%20David%20Atkin%2C%20an%20economics%20professor%20at%20MIT%20and%20one%20of%20the%20paper's%20coauthors.%20%26quot%3BIn%20terms%20of%20extrapolating%2C%20we%20do%20need%20to%20think%20carefully%20about%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20doesn't%20have%20all%20the%20answers%20for%20managers%20trying%20to%20navigate%20the%20messy%20middle%20of%20hybrid%20work%2C%20which%20remains%20the%20dominant%20model%20in%20the%20US.%20A%20recent%20large-scale%20analysis%20by%20consulting%20firm%20McKinsey%20%26amp%3B%20Co.%20of%20its%20own%20workforce%20found%20that%20about%2050%25%20of%20time%20spent%20on-site%20was%20the%20sweet%20spot%20for%20hybrid%20work.%20Anything%20more%20than%20that%20came%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20flexibility%20and%20focus%20time%20and%20didn't%20improve%20performance.%20Other%20randomized%20control%20trial%20research%20has%20found%20hybrid%20arrangements%20had%20no%20significant%20impact%20on%20productivity%2C%20though%20employees%20were%20substantially%20happier%20and%20less%20likely%20to%20leave.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMany%20of%20the%20articles%20that%20come%20out%20and%20criticize%20remote%20work%20and%20provide%20evidence%20that%20remote%20work%20is%20less%20productive%20are%20really%20talking%20about%20fully%20remote%20work%2C%20when%20really%20what%20matters%20for%20most%20of%20the%20people%20who%20can%20work%20from%20home%20is%20hybrid%2C%26quot%3B%20Barrero%20said.%C2%A0%20%26quot%3BIt's%20important%20to%20keep%20those%20nuances%20top%20of%20mind.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMIT's%20Atkin%20agrees.%20%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20the%20discussion%20now%20is%20on%20where%20we%20go%20on%20this%20work-from-home%20spectrum%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BDo%20we%20go%20all%20the%20way%20to%20full%20work-%20from-home%2C%20or%20to%20full%20work-in-the%20office%3F%20I%20think%20we'll%20end%20up%20somewhere%20in%20between.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691388960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Flthf7rkk_work-laptop-generic-bloomberg_625x300_07_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwfh-hires-18-less-productive-than-those-in-office-study-4275501%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20heated%20debate%