E%20for%20Nirdigantha%20%E2%80%93%20or%20%E2%80%98endless%20horizons%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20a%20theatre%20venture%20he%20will%20incubate%20in%20Mysore%20which%20will%20produce%2020%20plays%20and%20take%20them%20on%20tour%20in%20the%20next%20two%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaj%20blamed%20politicians%20for%20fostering%20divisions%20and%20inequality.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20dig%20a%20mosque%2C%20you%20will%20find%20a%20temple.%20If%20you%20dig%20a%20temple%2C%20you%20will%20find%20a%20Buddhist%20structure.%20How%20long%20are%20you%20going%20to%20keep%20digging%3F%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20asked.%20%E2%80%9CToday%20more%20than%20religion%20and%20caste%20it%20is%20money%20power%20that%20is%20driving%20politics%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20but%20this%20was%20the%20public%E2%80%99s%20money%20and%20we%20normally%20forget%20that.%20%E2%80%9CPoliticians%20come%20once%20in%20five%20years%20and%20go.%20We%20are%20permanent.%20Politics%20is%20us.%20It%20is%20our%20money.%20He%20flies%2C%20eats%20mushrooms%2C%20acts%20like%20a%20stationmaster.%20But%20it%20is%20our%20money.%E2%80%9D%20He%20called%20the%20rulers%20rakshasas%2C%20or%20demons%2C%20and%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20these%20%3Cspan%3Erakshasas%3C%2Fspan%3E%20are%20desperate%2C%20there%20is%20no%20telling%20what%20they%20will%20do.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReminded%20by%20Chishti%20of%20what%20he%20had%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20last%20year%20%E2%80%93%20that%20we%20are%20partying%20on%20a%20sinking%20ship%E2%80%A6%20the%20economy%2C%20prosperity%20etc%20is%20all%20sinking%20%E2%80%93%20Raj%20said%20that%20this%20was%20indeed%20the%20situation%20today.%20%E2%80%9CI%20want%20to%20ask%20those%20who%20speak%20of%20making%20India%20the%20Number%20One%20Economy%3A%20Where%20is%20Fraternity%20in%20your%20economy%3F%20Why%20is%20the%20one%20percent%20so%20far%20ahead%20of%20the%2099%25%3F%E2%80%9D.%20This%20was%20why%20the%20ship%20was%20sinking%2C%20he%20said.%20The%20person%20promising%20to%20make%20India%20number%20one%20will%20be%20sure%20to%20get%20away%20but%20the%20rest%20of%20us%20will%20go%20down%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Seema%20Chishti%20asked%20him%20what%20gives%20him%20hope%2C%20the%20actor%20said%20young%20people%20did.%20%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CYoungsters%20do.%20Their%20energy.%20Their%20sense%20of%20dignity%E2%80%A6%20I%20have%20seen%20young%20people%20at%20Seed%20Festivals%20in%20Karnataka.%E2%80%9D%20He%20said%20young%20people%20like%20Mohammed%20Zubair%20(a%20founder%20of%20AltNews)%2C%20the%20jailed%20activist%20Umar%20Khalid%20and%20the%20stand-up%20comic%20Kunal%20Kamra%20gave%20him%20hope.%20Above%20all%2C%20he%20said%2C%20people%20had%20to%20believe%20in%20their%20own%20strength.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShabnam%20Virmani%2C%20of%20the%20Kabir%20Project%20%E2%80%93%20which%20attempts%20to%20take%20a%20comprehensive%20look%20at%20Kabir%E2%80%99s%20thoughts%20and%20poetry%20%E2%80%93%20kick-started%20the%20conversation%20on%20fraternity%2C%20through%20music%20and%20verse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20she%20sang%20folk%20songs%20of%20Kabir%2C%20she%20struck%20the%20perfect%20note%20as%20a%20prelude%20to%20the%20discussion%20with%20Prakash%20Raj%20which%20followed.%20Virmani%2C%20whose%20work%20on%20Kabir%20is%20arguably%20the%20most%20multi-faceted%20in%20recent%20times%2C%20combining%20scholarship%2C%20art%20and%20performance%2C%20pointed%20to%20the%20poet-saint%E2%80%99s%20unique%20way%20of%20questioning%20identity%20and%20moving%20to%20get%20people%20to%20introspect.%20Kabir%2C%20she%20said%2C%20did%20not%20do%20slogans%20or%20skim%20on%20the%20surface%2C%20but%20pushed%20people%20to%20realise%20the%20vacuity%20of%20making%20so%20much%20of%20one%E2%80%99s%20social%20identity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-conte