ce%20Withdraws%20Support%20From%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%20Government%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F20124144%2FF1SovOrXoAA5F5U.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Kuki%20People%E2%80%99s%20Alliance%20(KPA)%20%E2%80%93%20a%20party%20with%20two%20sitting%20MLAs%20in%20the%20Manipur%20government%20and%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party-led%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20%E2%80%93%20on%20Sunday%20announced%20that%20it%20is%20withdrawing%20support%20from%20the%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20careful%20consideration%20of%20the%20current%20conflagration%2C%20the%20continued%20support%20for%20the%20incumbent%20government%20of%20Manipur%2C%20led%20by%20Chief%20Minister%20N%20Biren%20Singh%2C%20is%20no%20longer%20fructuous.%20Accordingly%2C%20the%20support%20of%20the%20KPA%20to%20the%20Government%20of%20Manipur%20is%20hereby%20withdrawn%20and%20can%20be%20considered%20null%20and%20void%2C%E2%80%9D%20KPA%20president%20Tongmang%20Haokip%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20on%20Sunday%20evening%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fnda-kuki-peoples-alliance-withdraws-support-biren-singh-govt-manipur-8879727%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20KPA%20MLAs%20currently%20in%20the%20Manipur%20assembly%20are%20Kimneo%20Hangshing%20and%20Chinlunthang%2C%20representing%20the%20Saikul%20and%20Singat%20constituencies%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20KPA%20is%20a%20new%20party%20%E2%80%93%20it%20was%20formed%20in%202022%20and%20contested%20its%20first%20elections%20in%20the%20same%20year.%20Members%20of%20the%20party%20had%20attended%20the%20NDA%20meet%20held%20in%20Delhi%20in%20July.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20eight%20other%20Kuki%20MLAs%20in%20the%20state%20assembly%2C%20all%20from%20the%20BJP.%20While%20they%20have%20openly%20criticised%20the%20chief%20minister%20for%20his%20handling%20of%20the%20ongoing%20ethnic%20conflict%2C%20they%20continue%20to%20be%20a%20part%20of%20the%20government.%20All%2010%20Kuki%20MLAs%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmanipur-violence-kuki-zomi-mlas-separate-administration%5C%22%3Eearlier%20urged%20the%20Union%20government%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20carve%20out%20a%20separate%20administration%20under%20the%20Indian%20constitution%20and%20let%20people%20from%20their%20community%20%E2%80%9Clive%20peacefully%20as%20neighbours%20with%20the%20state%20of%20Manipur%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Manipur%20assembly%20is%20supposed%20to%20convene%20on%20August%2021.%20The%20BJP%20MLA%20from%20Churachandpur%2C%20L.M.%20Khaute%2C%20has%20already%20said%20he%20will%20be%20unable%20to%20attend%20the%20session%20%E2%80%9Cin%20view%20of%20the%20prevailing%20law%20and%20order%20situation%E2%80%9D%2C%20PTI%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20three%20months%20have%20passed%20since%20ethnic%20conflict%20erupted%20in%20Manipur%20on%20May%203%2C%20and%20the%20violence%20is%20showing%20no%20signs%20of%20abating.%20On%20Saturday%2C%20six%20people%20were%20killed%20in%20fresh%20rounds%20of%20violence%20%E2%80%93%20leading%20the%20Union%20government%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fimphal%2Fmore-central-forces-sent-to-manipur-amid-meitei-outfits-appeal-to-boycott-biren-govt%2Farticleshow%2F102480622.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Esend%20800%20additional%20central%20security%20personnel%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Kuki%20groups%20have%20consistently%20held%20the%20Biren%20Singh%20government%20responsible%20for%20failing%20to%20protect%20their%20people%20and%20even%20encouraging%20the%20violence%2C%20Meitei%20groups%20too%20have%20openly%20expressed%20their%20unhappiness%20with%20the%20chief%20minister.%20The%20Coordinating%20Committee%20on%20Man