told%20Insider%20that%20Turkish%20drones%20have%20gained%20%26quot%3Bglobal%20recognition%26quot%3B%20due%20to%20their%20%26quot%3Baffordability%2C%20efficiency%2C%20and%20lethal%20capabilities%26quot%3B%20and%20documented%20successes%20over%20modern%20battlefields.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BFurthermore%2C%20the%20Turkish%20TB2%20has%20found%20its%20way%20to%20numerous%20countries%20across%20different%20continents%20and%20regions%2C%20including%20NATO%20and%20European%20Union%20members%2C%20as%20they%20come%20with%20fewer%20export%20restrictions%2C%26quot%3B%20Bakir%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%3ESuleyman%20Ozeren%2C%20a%20professorial%20lecturer%20at%20the%20American%20University%20and%20senior%20fellow%20at%20the%20Orion%20Policy%20Institute%2C%20said%20the%20Turkey-Saudi%20agreement%20represents%20more%20than%20merely%20purchasing%20drones%20or%20technology%20transfer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%3EIt's%20also%20%26quot%3Ba%20signifying%20moment%20that%20shows%20Erdogan's%20eagerness%20to%20make%20amends%20with%20Mohammed%20bin%20Salman%2C%26quot%3B%20Ozeren%20told%20Insider%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20Saudi%20crown%20prince.%20%26quot%3BErdogan%20sees%20Saudi%20Arabia%20as%20a%20critical%20actor%2C%20a%20remedy%20for%20Turkey's%20deep%20economic%20crisis%2C%20and%20a%20shortcut%20for%20his%20return%20to%20normalcy%20with%20the%20regional%20actors.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Turkey%20Bayraktar%20TB2%20Akinci%20drone%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64cc448e0b651c00193a66c6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Bayraktar%20TB2%2C%20left%2C%20and%20an%20Akinci%20on%20display%20at%20Ataturk%20Airport%20on%20May%201.%3Cp%3EAli%20Atmaca%2FAnadolu%20Agency%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%3EOzeren%20noted%20Turkey's%20dr