reunited%20with%20her%20family%2C%20for%20now.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Afghan%20villager%20was%20afraid%20the%20American%20soldiers%20might%20come.%20And%20one%20cool%20night%20in%20fall%2C%20as%20his%20children%20lay%20asleep%2C%20helicopters%20roared%20overhead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20first%20sound%20of%20gunshots%2C%20he%20yelled%20for%20his%20wife%20and%2010%20children%20to%20take%20cover.%20His%20young%20daughter%20grabbed%20her%20sleeping%20infant%20sister%20off%20the%20bed.%20Their%20mud%20compound%20exploded%2C%20and%20a%20blast%20sent%20a%20huge%20shock%20through%20the%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20small%20sister%20fell%20away%20from%20my%20arms%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20girl%2C%20now%20a%20teenager%2C%20whispered%2C%20so%20quietly%20she%20could%20barely%20be%20heard%20above%20the%20breeze.%20%26quot%3BThe%20wind%20blew%20her%20out%20of%20my%20hands.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20what%20exactly%20happened%20that%20night%20is%20at%20the%20center%20of%20a%20bitter%20international%20custody%20dispute%20over%20an%20orphaned%20baby%20found%20amid%20the%20rubble.%20The%20high-profile%20legal%20battle%20pits%20an%20Afghan%20family%20against%20an%20American%20one%2C%20and%20has%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fafghanistan-politics-united-states-government-virginia-children-97a4e2f4c38925d50e5511a3232974f0%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edrawn%20responses%20from%20the%20White%20House%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.documentcloud.org%2Fdocuments%2F23886733-doc-197-3-taliban-statement%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETaliban.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Afghan%20government%20and%20the%20International%20Committee%20of%20the%20Red%20Cross%20determined%20that%20the%20baby%20belonged%20to%20this%20Afghan%20villager.%20Friends%20and%20family%20say%20he%20was%20a%20farmer%2C%20not%20a%20militant.%20The%20Red%20Cross%20found%20surviving%20relatives%20and%20united%20her%20with%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20a%20US%20Marine%20attorney%2C%20Maj.%20Joshua%20Mast%2C%20believed%20he%20should%20get%20the%20girl%20instead.%20He%20insists%20that%20the%20child%20is%20the%20stateless%20orphan%20of%20foreign%20fighters%20who%20were%20living%20in%20an%20Al%20Qaeda%20compound%2C%20and%20convinced%20a%20rural%20Virginia%20judge%20to%20grant%20him%20an%20adoption%20from%207%2C000%20miles%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWere%20it%20not%20for%20this%20little%20girl%2C%20now%204%20years%20old%2C%20the%20events%20that%20began%20on%20the%20night%20of%20September%205%2C%202019%2C%20in%20this%20remote%2C%20impoverished%20region%20might%20have%20remained%20locked%20away%20among%20clandestine%20stories%20of%20the%20thousands%20of%20raids%20the%20American%20and%20Afghan%20militaries%20carried%20out%20during%20the%20long%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20once-secret%20documents%2C%20now%20filed%20in%20court%20records%2C%20reveal%20details%20that%20thrust%20this%20raid%20into%20an%20ongoing%20controversy%20over%20who%20the%20military%20killed%20when%20they%20blew%20down%20walls%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20night%20in%20Afghanistan%2C%20if%20those%20people%20were%20fighters%20or%20civilians%2C%20and%20whether%20the%20military%20ever%20tried%20to%20find%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Mast%20family%20has%20submitted%20a%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.documentcloud.org%2Fdocuments%2F23815515-declassified-mission-summary-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esummary%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20raid%20in%20a%20federal%20court%20case%2C%20an%20account%20Mast%20helped%20create%20after%20he%20said%20he%20%26quot%3Bpersonally%20read%20every%20page%20of%20the%20150%2B%20classified%20documents%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20operation.%20The%20summary%20describes%20how%20as%20many%20as%20six%20enemy%20fighters%20were%20killed%20and%20possibly%20one%20civilian.%20The%20only%20child%20the%20document%20mentions%20is%20the%20injured%20baby.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20survivors%20and%20villagers%20who%20pulled%20bodies%20from%20the%20rubble%20told%20The%20Associated%20Press%20that%20more%20than%2020%20people%20were%20killed%20that%20night.%20Among%20them%20were%20this%20local%20farmer%2C%20his%20wife%2C%20and%20five%20of%20their%20children%2C%20ages%204%20to%2015.%20The%20villagers%20said%20that%20after%20the%20raid%2C%20they%20also%20found%20four%20more%20of%20the%20farmer's%20children%20%E2%80%94%20three%20girls%20and%20a%20boy%20%E2%80%94%20covered%20in%20dirt%2C%20crying%20amid%20flames%20and%20ruins.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAttorneys%20for%20the%20federal%20government%20said%20the%20summary%20the%20Mast%20family%20submitted%20in%20court%20was%20written%20on%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.documentcloud.org%2Fdocuments%2F23894853-doc-214-main-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bpurported%26quot%3B%20military%20letterhead%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20%26quot%3Bdoes%20not%20appear%20to%20have%20been%20created%20or%20endorsed%20by%20the%20Department%20of%20Defense.%26quot%3B%20Nonetheless%2C%20they%20asked%20the%20court%20to%20seal%20it%20because%20they%20claim%20it%20contains%20government%20information%20the%20public%20should%20not%20see.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20'mission%20summary'%20document%20was%20created%20by%20Major%20Mast%20in%202019%20for%20use%20in%20his%20efforts%20to%20adopt%20the%20Afghan%20child%2C%20using%20his%20access%20to%20United%20States%20government%20information%20that%20he%20obtained%20through%20his%20Department%20of%20Defense%20employment%2C%20but%20does%20not%20necessarily%20reflect%20accurate%20or%20complete%20information%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20Defense%20Department%20official%20told%20the%20AP.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20military%20refuses%20to%20talk%20about%20its%20own%20account%20of%20the%20raid%2C%20and%20asked%20the%20AP%20to%20instead%20use%20a%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.documentcloud.org%2Fdocuments%2F23887877-decontrolled-mission-summary-2-may-2023_f%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eredacted%20version%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0that%20blacks%20out%20certain%20details%2C%20including%20any%20reference%20to%20civilian%20deaths.%20Several%20soldiers%20involved%20in%20the%20raid%2C%20who%20have%20testified%20in%20locked-door%20state%20court%20hearings%20about%20what%20happened%20there%2C%20declined%20to%20comment%2C%20and%20what%20they%20said%20on%20the%20witness%20stand%20remains%20sealed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20total%20cost%20of%20the%20war%20in%20civilian%20lives%20is%20impossible%20to%20pin%20down.%20The%20Defense%20Department%20estimates%2048%2C000%20Afghan%20civilians%20were%20killed%20and%20at%20least%2075%2C000%20injured%20between%202001%20and%202021%2C%20though%20the%20agency%20acknowledges%20the%20true%20toll%20is%20likely%20significantly%20higher.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENight%20raids%20have%20long%20been%20a%20particularly%20controversial%20tactic%2C%20said%20Patricia%20Gossman%2C%20associate%20Asia%20director%20at%20Human%20Rights%20Watch.%20Military%20investigations%20into%20who%20was%20killed%20in%20night%20raids%20were%20rare%2C%20and%20even%20more%20rarely%20made%20public.%20Gossman%20said%20a%20representative%20of%20the%20US%20military%20told%20her%20American%20soldiers%20hardly%20ever%20returned%20to%20the%20scene%20of%20a%20raid%20to%20see%20if%20civilians%20were%20killed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20said%20to%20us%2C%20'We%20can't%2C%20we%20can't%20go%20back%20there%20because%20we'd%20be%20a%20target%2C'%26quot%3B%20Gossman%20recalled.%20%26quot%3BBut%20then%20how%20do%20you%20ever%20know%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20AP%20spoke%20with%2012%20villagers%20who%20described%20what%20happened%20on%20the%20night%20of%20Sept.%205%2C%202019%2C%20including%20four%20who%20said%20they%20were%20the%20orphan's%20siblings%20and%20uncles.%20The%20AP%20has%20agreed%20not%20to%20name%20the%20village%20or%20the%20family%20out%20of%20fear%20of%20tribal%20conflict%20and%20retaliation%20from%20the%20Taliban%2C%20who%20now%20rule%20the%20country.%20But%20neighbors%20said%20they%20never%20saw%20anyone%20return%20to%20account%20for%20the%20dead%20and%20injured%2C%20including%20the%20children%2C%20or%20to%20verify%20if%20they%20were%20militants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20farmer's%20brother-in-law%20wept%20as%20he%20walked%20around%20the%20site%20of%20the%20raid%2C%20pointing%20out%20where%20he%20had%20found%20his%20surviving%20nephews%20and%20nieces%20and%20the%20mutilated%20corpses%20of%20his%20loved%20ones.%20He%20showed%20the%20AP%20where%20they%20lived%2C%20where%20they%20made%20fires%2C%20where%20they%20sat%2C%20where%20they%20ate.%20The%20farmer%20was%20around%2055%20or%2060%2C%20grew%20mung%20beans%2C%20corn%20and%20wheat%2C%20and%20was%20poor%20but%20generous%20enough%20to%20share%20any%20money%20he%20had%2C%20the%20brother-in-law%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%20that%20I%20come%20here%20and%20look%20at%20these%20places%2C%20they%20do%20not%20leave%20my%20eyes%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BMy%20heart%20is%20very%20sad.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EThe%20foreigners%20next%20door%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20in%20this%20rugged%20desert%2C%20families%20live%20among%20the%20ruins%20of%20a%2020-year%20war%20%E2%80%94%20rusted%20tanks%2C%20bombed-out%20houses%2C%20bullet-riddled%20buildings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDust%20kicks%20up%20from%20the%20wheels%20of%20motorcycles%20on%20dirt%20paths%2C%20where%20squat%20mud%20homes%20blend%20into%20mountains%20that%20stretch%20for%20miles%20in%20every%20direction.%20It%20is%20a%20hard%20life%3A%20There%20are%20no%20paved%20roads%2C%20no%20running%20water%20or%20electricity%2C%20no%20bathrooms%20or%20cell%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20locals%20said%20their%20tiny%20village%20was%20not%20targeted%20by%20the%20American%20military%20before%20September%202019%2C%20they%20feared%20the%20air%20strikes%2C%20night%20raids%20and%20fierce%20fighting%20decimating%20communities%20around%20them.%20Many%20raids%20happened%20in%20places%20like%20this%20%E2%80%94%20hard-to-reach%20outposts%2C%20far%20from%20city-based%20media%20outlets%20and%20human%20rights%20organizations%20that%20might%20look%20into%20civilian%20deaths.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbout%20200%20people%20scratch%20out%20a%20living%20raising%20animals%20and%20farming%20on%20the%20green%20fertile%20patch%20of%20land%20alongside%20the%20river.%20The%20farmer%20and%20his%20family%20tended%20to%20their%20goats%20and%20sheep%20in%20the%20courtyard%20of%20their%20home%2C%20villagers%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20home%20was%20a%20windowless%20one-story%20compound%20of%20mud%20and%20straw.%20Like%20many%20in%20this%20conservative%20region%2C%20women%20stayed%20within%20the%20walls%20for%20most%20of%20their%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYears%20and%20ages%20can%20be%20difficult%20to%20calculate%20in%20Afghanistan%2C%20which%20uses%20different%20calendars%20than%20much%20of%20the%20world%2C%20but%20neighbors%20said%20the%20farmer%20and%20his%20family%20had%20lived%20there%20for%20a%20long%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENeighbor%20Abdul%20Khaliq%20said%20he%20had%20known%20the%20farmer%20for%20more%20than%2020%20years%2C%20and%20described%20him%20as%20kind%20and%20amiable.%20%26quot%3BHe%20was%20a%20very%20good%20person%2C%26quot%3B%20Khaliq%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20farmer's%20wife%20was%20younger%2C%20around%2040%2C%20and%20they'd%20been%20married%20for%20about%2025%20years.%20She%20was%20the%20daughter%20of%20an%20imam%20at%20a%20local%20mosque%2C%20and%20remained%20close%20to%20her%20family.%20She%20had%20a%20sense%20of%20humor%20%E2%80%94%20her%20brother%20said%20she%20would%20laugh%20as%20she%20teased%20him%20for%20not%20visiting%20often%20enough.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20way%20the%20AP%20could%20independently%20verify%20who%20the%20baby's%20parents%20were.%20Identification%20documents%20such%20as%20birth%20certificates%20aren't%20issued%20in%20this%20remote%20region%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20for%20women%20and%20girls%20%E2%80%94%20and%20few%20have%20cell%20phones%20or%20cameras.%20The%20AP%20has%20located%20no%20records%20of%20the%20birth%20of%20the%20farmer's%20baby%20or%20photographs%20of%20her%20with%20the%20family%20before%20the%20raid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Afghan%20government%20claimed%20the%20child%2C%20and%20the%20U.S.%20government%20agreed%20that%20the%20girl%2C%20who%20is%20referred%20to%20in%20court%20records%20as%20%26quot%3BBaby%20Doe%2C%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.documentcloud.org%2Fdocuments%2F23894860-doc-131-government-answer%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebelonged%20to%20an%20Afghan%20family%3A%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%26quot%3BBaby%20Doe%20is%20a%20citizen%20of%20Afghanistan%20with%20biological%20family%20in%20Afghanistan%2C%26quot%3B%20attorneys%20for%20the%20federal%20government%20wrote%20in%20court%20filings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20Masts%20strongly%20disagree.%20Several%20foreign%20families%20arrived%20in%20the%20village%20around%202017%20and%20settled%20into%20a%20home%20next%20to%20the%20Afghan%20farmer%20and%20his%20family%2C%20neighbors%20said.%20These%20men%2C%20women%20and%20children%20shared%20a%20wall%2C%20but%20kept%20to%20themselves%20and%20spoke%20an%20unfamiliar%20language%2C%20villagers%20told%20the%20AP.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20light-skinned%2C%20bearded%20foreigners%20were%20a%20source%20of%20gossip.%20Some%20neighbors%20speculated%20they%20were%20from%20another%2C%20faraway%20Afghan%20province%2C%20or%20Turkey%2C%20or%20%26quot%3Bthe%20West.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELocal%20mechanic%20Abdul%20Rahim%2C%2025%2C%20said%20the%20foreigners%20often%20brought%20their%20cars%2C%20trucks%20and%20motorcycles%20to%20be%20fixed%20at%20his%20shop.%20No%20matter%20where%20they%20came%20from%2C%20one%20thing%20was%20clear%20to%20Rahim%3A%20They%20liked%20their%20weapons.%20They'd%20clean%20their%20guns%20while%20he%20fixed%20their%20cars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20tried%20very%20hard%20to%20talk%20to%20them%2C%20but%20I%20couldn't%20understand%20the%20language%2C%26quot%3B%20Rahim%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere%20was%20never%20a%20fight%20or%20quarrel%20with%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Afghanistan%2C%20hospitality%20is%20of%20foremost%20importance%2C%20and%20nobody%20confronted%20the%20visiting%20foreigners.%20The%20locals%20said%20they%20were%20friendly%2C%20but%20cautious.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20farmer%20told%20his%20brother-in-law%20he%20was%20considering%20moving%20his%20family%20to%20another%20relative's%20house%20nearby.%20He%20was%20frightened%20that%20the%20military%20might%20come%20for%20the%20foreigners%20so%20close%20to%20his%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%26quot%3BThere%20were%20red%20fires%26quot%3B%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20day%20of%20the%20raid%20unfolded%20like%20any%20other%3B%20the%20family%20fed%20corn%20and%20grass%20to%20the%20animals%20in%20the%20morning%20and%20cooked%20potatoes%20for%20lunch.%20They%20had%20no%20idea%20that%20U.S.%20and%20Afghan%20forces%20were%20loading%20up%20in%20helicopters%20to%20head%20toward%20their%20village.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20soldiers%20were%20targeting%20three%20men%20in%20two%20compounds%20believed%20to%20be%20al-Qaida-affiliated%20fighters%20from%20neighboring%20Turkmenistan%2C%20according%20to%20the%20summary%20the%20Masts%20submitted%20in%20court.%20As%20soldiers%20approached%2C%20they%20called%20out%2C%20offering%20the%20people%20inside%20a%20chance%20to%20surrender%2C%20according%20to%20the%20summary.%20One%20man%20was%20detained.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERahim%2C%20the%20local%20mechanic%2C%20said%20he%20had%20just%20fallen%20asleep%20under%20a%20tree%20outside%20a%20friend's%20home%20when%20he%20heard%20someone%20shouting%20in%20Pashto%2C%20%26quot%3Bstop%2C%20don't%20run.%26quot%3B%20Awakening%20beside%20him%2C%20Mohammad%20Zaman%20remembers%20door-to-door%20knocks%20with%20orders%20%26quot%3Bnot%20to%20move%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bnot%20to%2