0in%20the%201860s.%20Although%20their%20numbers%20were%20minuscule%20when%20compared%20to%20today%E2%80%99s%20figures%2C%20newspaper%20readers%20from%20the%20last%20decades%20of%20the%2019h%20century%20were%20conversant%20about%20the%20phenomenon%20of%20%E2%80%98music-before-mosque%20riots%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjulianlynch.bandcamp.com%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EJulian%20Lynch%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%93%20musician%2C%20composer%2C%20ethnomusicologist%2C%20researchers%2C%20and%20music%20teacher%20all%20rolled%20into%20one%20%E2%80%93%20wrote%20that%20this%20category%20of%20riots%2C%20was%20the%20result%20of%20%E2%80%9Cdeliberate%20display%20of%20a%20musical%20procession%2C%20usually%20accompanying%20a%20Hindu%20festival%2C%20in%20front%20of%20a%20Muslim%20place%20of%20worship%2C%20causing%20offence%20and%2C%20very%20often%2C%20violence.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20would%20know%20this%20issue%20very%20well%20having%20completed%20a%20PhD%20thesis%20from%20the%20Department%20of%20Anthropology%20with%20focus%20on%20Ethnomusicology%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Wisconsin-Madison%20in%202020.%20He%20spent%20well%20over%20a%20decade%20researching%20the%20subject.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESocial%20media%20posts%20on%20the%20violence%20in%20Nuh%20underscored%20that%20the%20acts%20of%20provocation%20were%20justified%20by%20asserting%20that%20Hinduism%20calls%20for%20music%20being%20performed%20on%20virtually%20every%20occasion.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20dwelling%20on%20this%20cause%20of%20conflict%20between%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mkgandhi.org%2Fg_communal%2Fchap13.htm%5C%22%3EMahatma%20Gandhi%20observed%3A%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%9CNot%20a%20single%20Hindu%20religious%20ceremony%20can%20be%20performed%20without%20the%20accompaniment%20of%20music.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20immediate%20context%2C%20neither%20the%20VHP-Bajrang%20Dal%E2%80%99s%20insistence%20to%20take%20out%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EShobha%20Yatra%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20the%20occasion%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ESawan%20Somvar%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(Monday%20in%20the%20Hindu%20month%20of%20Sawan)%20nor%20the%20%3Cem%3ERam%20Navami%3C%2Fem%3E%20processions%20earlier%20in%20April%20%E2%80%93%20which%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Fopinion%2Fram-navami-violence-in-ramzan-month-shows-future-is-stark-its-karo-ya-maro-for-india-now%2F1519159%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Etriggered%20communal%20violence%20in%20seven%20states%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20during%20the%20Ramzan%20%E2%80%93%20were%20religious%20ceremonies%20per%20se.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EInstead%2C%20music%20on%20such%20occasions%20is%20used%20to%20display%20Hindu%20might.%20It%20is%20a%20vehicle%20to%20establish%20what%20Lynch%20calls%2C%20the%20community%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cdomination%20and%20territoriality%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Friots-and-wrong-communal-violence-raises-electoral-stakes-but-who-gains-from-polarisation%5C%22%3ERiots%20and%20Wrong%3A%20Communal%20Violence%20Raises%20Electoral%20Stakes%20but%20Who%20Gains%20From%20Polarisation%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20message%20to%20Muslims%20when%20passing%20through%20Muslim%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eilaaqe%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20or%20localities%2C%20what%20academic%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Farticle%2Fbeyond-business%2Fthe-ilaqa-syndrome-121021501431_1.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ENazima%20Parveen%20detailed%20in%20her%20in-depth%20book%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EContested%20Homelands%3A%20Politics%20of%20Space%20and%20Identity%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20is%20that%20of%20majoritarian%20hegemony.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMusic%20played%20by%20Hindus%20in%20processions%2C%20like%20in%20Nuh%2C%20is%20not%20a%20mark%20of%20devotion.%20Instead%2C%20the%20objective%20is%20to%20convey%20Hindu%20power%20to%20march-in%2C%20at%20will%2C%20into%20Muslim-dominated%20localities%20and%20play%20music%20outside%20mosques%20only%20to%20slight%20them.%20This%20is%20done%20with%20full%20knowledge%20that%20Islam%20considers%20music%20as%20morally%20improper%20and%20thereby%20proscribes%20its%20performance.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20intention%20was%20to%20provoke%20and%20cock%20a%20snook%20at%20Muslims%20in%20the%20late%20nineteenth%20century.%20It%20remains%20the%20same%20even%20now.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20his%20thesis%20and%20a%20short%20paper%20that%20preceded%20it%2C%20Lynch%20drew%20attention%20to%20an%201882%20report%20from%20Salem%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20by%20an%20anonymous%20correspondent%20of%20The%20Pioneer.%20The%20reporter%20visited%20the%20city%20after%20a%20violent%20series%20of%20riots%20triggered%20by%20music%20played%20by%20those%20in%20the%20procession%20as%20they%20passed%20by%20the%20mosque.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20newspaper%20article%20mentioned%20bodies%20of%20infants%2C%20men%20and%20women%20%E2%80%93%20all%20Muslim%2C%20strewn%20in%20the%20locality.%20Their%20houses%20and%20the%20mosque%20were%20burning%20or%20%E2%80%9Crazed%20to%20the%20ground%E2%80%A6%20There%20were%20corpses%20on%20all%20sides%E2%80%9D.%20The%20unnamed%20reporter%20also%20saw%20%E2%80%9Cdead%20pigs%20thrown%20in%20with%20the%20corpses%20of%20Muhammadan%20children.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20stray%20incidents%20became%20part%20of%20the%20emerging%20Hindu%20nationalistic%20toolkit%20in%20the%201890s%20with%20Bal%20Gangadhar%20Tilak%20consciously%20converting%20Ganesh%20Chaturthi%20from%20being%20%E2%80%9Ca%20devotional%20festival%20celebrated%20in%20honour%20of%20the%20god%20Ganesh%E2%80%A6%20to%20a%20public%20spectacle%20with%20strong%20political%20motivations.%E2%80%9D%20This%20happened%20in%201894%2C%20a%20year%20after%20the%201893%20Bombay%20riots.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20riots%20between%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims%20were%20triggered%20in%20August%20that%20year%20when%20%E2%80%9CHindu%20ritual%20music%E2%80%9D%20was%20played%20while%20Muslims%20offered%20the%20Friday%20afternoon%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Enamaz%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Lynch%20wrote%20that%20this%20incident%20%E2%80%9Cprompted%20particularly%20fervent%20editorializing%20from%20the%20Marathi-language%20newspaper%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EKesari%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20especially%20from%20the%20publication%E2%80%99s%20founder%2C%20Brahmin%20leader%20Bal%20Gangadhar%20Tilak.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20less%20than%20two%20months%2C%20Tilak%20and%20other%20Brahmin%20leaders%20of%20the%20Bombay%20Presidency%20began%20planning%20the%20%E2%80%9Cgrand%20reinvention%E2%80%9D%20of%20Ganesh%20Chaturthi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%201894%2C%20when%20the%20festival%20was%20first%20celebrated%20as%20planned%2C%20it%20effectively%20converted%20a%20modest%20private%20observance%20and%20localised%20collective%20immersions%20into%20a%20very%20public%20and%20more%20extravagant%20%E2%80%98event%E2%80%99.%20The%20celebrations%20have%20become%20more%20ostentatious%20with%20time%20as%20new%20features%20got%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUntil%201893%2C%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims%20used%20to%20celebrate%20festivals%20with%20one%20another.%20Hindus%20joined%20the%20Muharram%20festivities%20and%20contributed%20money%20to%20local%20groups%20besides%20offering%20their%20services%20as%20musicians%20for%20which%20they%20were%20paid.%20Tilak%20called%20for%20the%20boycott%20of%20Muharram%20by%20Hindus.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELynch%20wrote%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20anti-Muslim%20undercurrents%20of%20the%20public%20Ganesh%20Chaturthi%20found%20more%20overt%20expression%20in%20Tilak%E2%80%99s%20calls%20in%201894%20for%20Hindus%20to%20boycott%20celebrations%20of%20Muharram.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20also%20cited%20an%201895%20government%20report%20that%20stated%20that%20there%20had%20been%20%E2%80%9Cmore%20Hindu%20than%20Muhammadan%20Tabuts%2C%20and%20on%20the%20last%20day%20(the%20day%20of%20immersion)%20by%20far%20the%20greater%20part%20of%20the%20procession%20was%20entirely%20Hindu%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETilak%E2%80%99s%20anger%20was%20because%20Muslims%20had%20forgotten%20their%20%E2%80%9C%20long-standing%20friendship%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cbegan%20a%20regular%20campaign%20of%20harassing%20Hindu%20religious%20mendicants.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20colonial%20regime%20got%20the%20opportunity%20they%20sought%20to%20divide%20the%20people%20and%20tighten%20their%20grip.%20The%20Public%20and%20Judicial%20Department%20felt%20that%20the%201894%20Ganpati%20festival%20would%20serve%20%E2%80%9Cas%20a%20counter%20blast%20to%20the%20Muharram.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELynch%20was%20of%20the%20opinion%20that%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccrucial%20aspect%20of%20Tilak%E2%80%99s%20marketing%20of%20Ganeshotsav%20as%20a%20replacement%20for%20Muharram%20involved%20the%20design%20of%20key%20elements%20in%20the%20festival%20to%20directly%20mimic%20those%20of%20Muharram.%E2%80%9D%20This%20included%20music%20and%20dancing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20methods%20succeeded%20and%20like%20the%20Ganesh%20Chaturthi%2C%20the%20Durga%20Puja%20in%20Bengal%20also%20was%20converted%20from%20being%20a%20mainly%20a%20domestic%20affair%20to%20public%20pujas%20in%20community%20places.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERiots%20between%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims%20became%20a%20recurring%20phenomenon%20and%20this%20faultline%20became%20visible%20in%20Nagpur%20too%2C%20the%20eventual%20seat%20of%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS).%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%201923%2C%20its%20eventual%20founder%2C%20Keshav%20Baliram%20Hedgewar%20declared%20his%20intention%20to%20breach%20a%201914%20agreement%20of%20not%20playing%20music%20in%20front%20of%20mosques%20during%20the%20Ganesh%20immersion%20procession%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20festival.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20him%2C%20the%20right%20to%20play%20music%20was%20not%20a%20trivial%20matter%20but%20a%20manifestation%20of%20%E2%80%98Hindu%20strength%E2%80%99.%20When%20the%20local%20administration%20clamped%20an%20embargo%20on%20playing%20music%2C%20Hedgewar%20convinced%20local%20Hindu%20leaders%20to%20postpone%20the%20immersion%20of%20Ganesh%20idols%20that%20year.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20decision%20and%20an%20effort%20to%20play%20music%20in%20front%20of%20mosques%20was%20prevented%20by%20the%20administration%20which%20led%20to%20a%20protest.%20In%20the%20annals%20of%20the%20RSS%2C%20this%20agitation%20is%20called%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EDindi%20Satyagraha%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20referring%20to%20a%20group%2C%20or%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Edindi%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20singing%20songs%20%E2%80%93%20ostensibly%20devotional%20but%20acting%20to%20create%20confrontation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EReports%20mention%20that%20B.S.%20Moonje%20was%20the%20satyagraha%E2%80%99s%20chief%20planner%20and%20Hedgewar%20was%20the%20%E2%80%9Cstormtrooper.%E2%80%9D%20More%20than%20half%20a%20decade%20later%2C%20Moonje%20would%20visit%20Italy%2C%20meet%20Benito%20Mussolini%20and%20visit%20numerous%20fascist%20training%20centres.%20On%20his%20return%20he%20spoke%20about%20replicating%20several%20facilities%20he%20saw%20in%20Italy.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20communal%20clashes%20continued%20in%20Nagpur%20and%20in%20September%201925%2C%20Hedgewar%20established%20the%20RSS.%20In%20many%20ways%2C%20%E2%80%98music-before-mosque%E2%80%99%20was%20one%20of%20the%20primary%20reasons%20that%20eventually%20led%20to%20the%20formation%20of%20the%20RSS.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20time%2C%20the%20music-before-mosque%20changed%2C%20like%20in%201989%20in%20Bhagalpur%2C%20slogans%20were%20shouted%20in%20front%20of%20a%20mosque%20during%20that%20year%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EShila%20Yatra%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20when%20specially%20consecrated%20bricks%20were%20transported%20to%20Ayodhya.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20led%20to%20one%20of%20the%20worst%20communal%20riots%20engulfing%20almost%20the%20entire%20district.%20Several%20dossiers%20can%20be%20compiled%20of%20instances%20when%20the%20Sangh%20parivar%20organisations%20forced%20communal%20violence%20with%20the%20same%20tactics.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20now%2C%20as%20the%20events%20in%20Nuh%20show%2C%20the%20nearly%20150-year-old%20ploy%20is%20still%20being%20used.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3ENilanjan%20Mukhopadhyay%E2%80%99s%20latest%20book%20is%20The%20Demolition%20and%20the%20Verdict%3A%20Ayodhya%20and%20the%20Project%20to%20Reconfigure%20India.%20His%20other%20books%20include%20The%20RSS%3A%20Icons%20of%20the%20Indian%20Right%20and%20Narendra%20Modi%3A%20The%20Man%2C%20The%20Times.%20He%20tweets%20at%20%40NilanjanUdwin%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691321916000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F01204406%2Fdamaged.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fhow-a-150-year-old-ploy-to-incite-religious-violence-is-still-used-in-india%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%