0years%20ago%2C%20kicking%20up%20an%20armed%20civil%20disobedience%20movement%20to%20restore%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20press%20statement%20by%20the%20state%20government%20on%20July%2029%20had%20said%20that%20the%20process%20of%20identifying%20%E2%80%9Cillegal%20migrants%E2%80%9D%20would%20be%20carried%20out%20in%20all%20districts.%20Joint%20secretary%20at%20the%20state%20home%20department%2C%20Peter%20Salam%2C%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fnorth-east-india%2Fmanipur%2Fmanipur-starts-capturing-biometric-data-of-illegal-immigrants-from-myanmar-8866925%2F%5C%22%3Etold%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20district%20heads%20have%20been%20asked%20to%20identify%20%E2%80%9Call%20illegal%20migrants%E2%80%9D%20under%20their%20respective%20jurisdictions.%20He%20said%20over%202%2C500%20%E2%80%9Cillegal%20immigrants%E2%80%9D%20had%20been%20identified%20thus%20far%2C%20of%20whom%20Naga-dominated%20Chandel%20district%20had%20the%20highest%20at%20around%201%2C050.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20week%2C%20reacting%20to%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20number%20in%20Chandel%2C%20the%20influential%20civil%20society%20group%20(CSO)%20United%20Naga%20Council%20(UNC)%20had%20said%20there%20is%20an%20%E2%80%9Curgent%20need%E2%80%9D%20to%20update%20the%20National%20Register%20of%20Citizens%20in%20the%20state.%20Accusing%20the%20MHA%20of%20facilitating%20the%20%E2%80%9Cinflux%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20UNC%20in%20a%20press%20statement%20had%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20alarming%20to%20learn%20the%20fresh%20influx%20of%20illegal%20immigrant%2C%20Myanmarese%20nationals%20along%20the%20Indo-Myanmar%20border%20in%20Chandel%20district%20to%20the%20tune%20of%20718%20persons%20in%20just%20a%20day%2C%20as%20per%20the%20report%20of%20Assam%20Rifles%2029%20sector%2C%20dated%20July%2023%2C%202023.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAside%20from%20the%20UNC%2C%20several%20powerful%20Meitei%20CSOs%20have%20demanded%20a%20stop%20to%20the%20inflow%20of%20refugees%20from%20across%20the%20international%20border.%20During%20the%20ongoing%20conflict%20of%20the%20Meitei%20community%20with%20the%20Kuki%20community%20which%20share%20ethnic%20affinities%20with%20the%20Chin%20people%20of%20Myanmar%2C%20not%20just%20the%20Meitei%20CSOs%20but%20the%20state%20chief%20minister%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%20also%20accused%20them%20of%20harbouring%20%E2%80%9Cillegal%20immigrants%E2%80%9D%20from%20that%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%201%2C600-km-long%20international%20border%20with%20Myanmar%2C%20Manipur%20shares%20390%20km%20while%20500%20km%20are%20along%20Mizoram.%20The%20border%20is%20porous%20as%20India%20has%20a%20free%20movement%20regime%20with%20Myanmar%2C%20which%20permits%20people%20residing%20on%20either%20side%20to%20travel%2017%20km%20on%20both%20sides%20without%20visa%20restrictions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20Nagaland%20and%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20also%20share%20border%20with%20Myanmar%2C%20the%20arrival%20of%20refugees%20has%20been%20noted%20officially%20only%20in%20Manipur%20and%20Mizoram.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691313825000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F05163830%2FFfSeJrYVIAATp3gfinal.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fmanipur-mizoram-start-collecting-biometrics-of-rohingya-refugees-on-mhas-orders%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20the%20MHA%20asked%20these%20states%20to%20complete%20the%20process%20by%20September%2030%2C%20the%20Zoramthanga%20government%20has%20informed%20the%20MHA%20that%20it%20would%20not%20be%20able%20to%20complete%20the%20task%20by%20this%20deadline.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A24%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fmanipur-mizoram-start-collecting-biometrics-of-rohingya-refugees-on-mhas-orders%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Barbie'%2C%20'Oppenheimer'%2C%20and%20Why%20We%20Shouldn't%20Avert%20Our%20Eyes%20from%20Hiroshima%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F06144038%2Fc3326679-1002-4aa3-9359-f378e03f0df5_3600x3600.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EToday%2C%20August%206%2C%20marks%20the%2078th%20anniversary%20of%20the%20destruction%20of%20Hiroshima%20by%20an%20atomic%20bomb%20dropped%20on%20the%20city%20by%20the%20United%20States%20during%20the%20Second%20World%20War.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETokyo%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20America%E2%80%99s%20pathologies%20are%2C%20in%20my%20experience%2C%20more%20apparent%20(though%20no%20less%20troubling)%20from%20afar.%20The%20simultaneous%20release%20of%20the%20films%20%3Cem%3EBarbie%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3EOppenheimer%3C%2Fem%3E%20resulting%20in%20the%20distasteful%20but%20hardly%20surprising%20%E2%80%9CBarbenheimer%E2%80%9D%20meme%20is%20a%20case%20in%20point%3A%20America%E2%80%99s%20twin%20obsessions%20of%20how%20it%20looks%20in%20the%20mirror%20and%20how%20it%E2%80%99s%20remembered%20in%20the%20history%20books%20have%20collided%20head%20on%2C%20leaving%20a%20twisted%20mess%20of%20wreckage%20%E2%80%93%20however%20harmless%20at%20this%20point%20%E2%80%93%20revealing%20more%20about%20our%20culture%20and%20ourselves%20than%20we%20care%20to%20admit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20someone%20who%20has%20yet%20to%20see%20either%20film%2C%20I%E2%80%99ll%20withhold%20judgment%20on%20the%20filmmakers%E2%80%99%20vision%20and%20their%20success%20or%20failure%20in%20realising%20it%20on%20the%20big%20screen.%20Like%20last%20year%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20happy%20to%20report%20that%20I%E2%80%99m%20spending%20much%20of%20this%20summer%20in%20Japan%20visiting%20family%2C%20meaning%20my%2011-year-old%20son%E2%80%99s%20grandparents%20and%20a%20whole%20host%20of%20welcoming%20uncles%2C%20aunts%2C%20cousins%2C%20nephews%2C%20nieces%2C%20and%20neighbours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%2C%20it%20should%20be%20said%2C%20are%20exactly%20the%20kind%20of%20ordinary%20Japanese%20folks%20that%20director%20Christopher%20Nolan%20chose%20to%20leave%20out%20of%20his%20film%20about%20the%20%E2%80%9Cmastermind%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20atomic%20bomb%2C%20and%20precisely%20the%20people%20who%20suffered%20and%20died%20in%20the%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20when%20the%20US%20dropped%20atomic%20bombs%20on%20Hiroshima%20and%20Nagasaki.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20respect%20Nolan%20as%20a%20filmmaker%20and%2C%20once%20again%2C%20will%20withhold%20judgment%20until%20I%20see%20the%20film.%20Being%20in%20Japan%20%E2%80%93%20which%20has%20yet%20to%20set%20a%20release%20date%20for%20%3Cem%3EOppenheimer%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20but%20is%20expected%20to%20later%20this%20year%20after%20the%20August%206%20and%20August%209%20anniversaries%20of%20the%201945%20atomic%20bombings%20%E2%80%93%20I%20haven%E2%80%99t%20had%20the%20opportunity%20to%20see%20his%20film%2C%20which%20I%20certainly%20will%20see.%20I%20have%2C%20however%2C%20had%20the%20opportunity%20to%20visit%20Hiroshima%20on%20a%20number%20of%20occasions%2C%20first%20as%20a%20young%20journalist%20nearly%2030%20years%20ago%2C%20and%20last%20summer%20with%20my%20wife%20and%20son.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20that%20first%20visit%20in%201995%2C%20not%20long%20before%20the%2050th%20anniversary%20of%20the%20bombing%20of%20Hiroshima%2C%20I%20had%20the%20great%20honour%20of%20interviewing%20Yoshito%20Matsushige%20%E2%80%93%20a%20photographer%20for%20the%20local%20newspaper%20who%20was%20just%202.7%20kilometres%20from%20the%20hypocentre%20when%20the%20blast%20occurred%20at%208%3A15%20that%20August%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20wrote%20last%20August%20in%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flink.sbstck.com%2Fredirect%2Fdd02cca1-f829-4d40-b643-b2141289fd13%3Fj%3DeyJ1IjoiMWc3ZDkifQ.ANHu2vRAyuFpjv7uiZBbU4uAYv19NWdGMb8wTAqqIz8%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Flink.sbstck.com%2Fredirect%2Fdd02cca1-f829-4d40-b6