%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F05103945%2FIMG_1783.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mrinal%20Pande%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22378%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F05103945%2FIMG_1783.jpg%20525w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F05103945%2FIMG_1783-246x300.jpg%20246w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-642789%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22461%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20obvious%20from%20the%20TV%20debates%20%2Cwith%20party%20spokespersons%20and%20anchors%20bellowing%20at%20each%20other%2C%20how%20widely%20and%20deep%20this%20virus%20for%20%E2%80%98others%E2%80%99%20has%20seeped%20within%20the%20popular%20view%20of%20minorities%20in%20Amritkaal.%20It%20was%20contempt%20for%20a%20group%2C%20not%20rage%20against%20certain%20individuals%2C%20that%20drove%20the%20killer%20Railway%20Police%20Force%20jawan%20to%20shoot%20down%20four%20human%20beings.%20In%20the%20video%20clips%20that%20surfaced%20thereafter%2C%20you%20heard%20no%20loud%20remonstrations%20from%20fellow%20travellers.%20The%20only%20one%20who%20spoke%20up%2C%20his%20superior%2C%20had%20been%20gunned%20down%20while%20people%20were%20simply%20gaping%20or%20making%20videos%20of%20the%20gory%20scene.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20same%20virus%20of%20contempt%20surfaced%20during%20the%20communal%20clashes%20in%20Nuh%20in%20Haryana.%20You%20saw%20young%20men%20in%20saffron%20raising%20slogans%2C%20picking%20up%20bricks%20and%20hurling%20them%2C%20firing%20from%20guns%20at%20scared%2C%20huddled%20folk%20pelting%20stones%20to%20stop%20them%20from%20roofs.%20The%20reporters%20and%20onlookers%20hiding%20in%20some%20safe%20perches%20simply%20kept%20recording%20it%20for%20primetime%20news%2C%20as%20though%20what%20was%20happening%20was%20not%20real%20rioting%2C%20looting%2C%20arson%20and%20murder%2C%20but%20an%20exciting%20video%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20virus%20of%20contempt%20first%20created%20in%20an%20unknown%20lab%20somewhere%20belongs%20to%20mind-manipulating%20power%20groups%20who%20weaponise%20fear%20and%20turn%20revenge%20into%20a%20mindless%20game%20for%20their%20young%20followers.%20The%20followers%20in%20garish%20costumes%2C%20flourishing%20their%20guns%2C%20trishuls%2C%20swords%20and%20%3Cem%3Elathis%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20then%20parade%20on%20the%20streets%20like%20a%20militia%2C%20chanting%20provocative%20slogans.%20Through%20their%20young%2C%20the%20virus%20then%20enters%20entire%20families%2C%20schools%2C%20colleges%2C%20markets%20and%20%3Cem%3Emohalla%3C%2Fem%3E%20groups%2C%20and%20of%20late%20even%20some%20serving%20in%20the%20armed%20protection%20forces.%20Communally%20sensitive%20areas%20then%20become%20a%20focus%20of%20contempt%3A%20areas%20where%20sub-humans%20live.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChetan%20Kumar%2C%20the%20constable%20now%20in%20custody%2C%20is%20an%20example%20of%20a%20carrier%20of%20this%20fatal%20disease.%20Maybe%20in%20his%20eyes%20those%20that%20he%20shot%20were%20deserving%20of%20extermination.%20Look%20at%20Chetan%20Kumar%20standing%20legs%20apart%2C%20gazing%20down%20coldly%20at%20his%20victims%20gasping%20for%20breath.%20He%20can%20be%20seen%20strutting%20about%20from%20bogie%20to%20bogie%2C%20gunning%20down%20men%2C%20shouting%20slogans%20that%20if%20the%20likes%20of%20them%20wished%20to%20live%20in%20India%2C%20they%20must%20accept%20leaders%20Kumar%20personally%20deems%20to%20be%20worthy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReports%20quickly%20followed%20from%20the%20Railway%20Protection%20Force%20that%20first%20said%20the%20fellow%20was%20mentally%20unsound%20and%20was%20undergoing%20treatment.%20These%20statements%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Frailways-denies-rpf-man-who-killed-boss-three-muslims-was-mentally-unstable-then-rescinds-denial%5C%22%3Ewere%20then%20denied%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20it%20was%20realised%20that%20handing%20a%20gun%20to%20a%20mentally%20unstable%20man%20could%20be%20construed%20legally%20as%20an%20act%20of%20criminal%20negligence.%20Then%20this%20denial%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Frailways-denies-rpf-man-who-killed-boss-three-muslims-was-mentally-unstable-then-rescinds-denial%5C%22%3Ewas%20withdrawn%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20is%20no%20mad%20man.%20It%20was%20sheer%20contempt%20he%20is%20showing%20towards%20the%20rule%20of%20law%2C%20towards%20fellow%20humans.%20He%20was%2C%20for%20heaven%E2%80%99s%20sake%2C%20armed%20to%20protect.%20Contempt%2C%20you%20realise%2C%20is%20deadlier%20than%20simple%20hate.%20Hate%20has%20a%20target%20and%20a%20vendetta-driven%20agenda%20that%20it%20follows%20with%20cunning%2C%20keeping%20itself%20hidden%20with%20a%20mask%2C%20a%20helmet%20or%20even%20a%20%3Cem%3Egamcha%3C%2Fem%3E%20wrapped%20around%20the%20face.%20One%20carrying%20the%20virus%20of%20contempt%20does%20not%20care.%20He%20is%20whimsical%20and%20can%20whip%20out%20a%20pistol%20to%20shoot%20to%20kill%2C%20entirely%20unmoved%20by%20moral%20or%20legal%20compunctions.%20In%20his%20eyes%20the%20ones%20he%20killed%20at%20random%20were%20not%20certifiably%20patriotic%20worshippers%20of%20The%20Regime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20contempt%20virus%20was%20once%20again%20in%20full%20view%20in%20the%20communal%20rioting%20in%20Haryana.%20Every%20one%20knows%20that%20Nuh%20(earlier%20Mewat)%20is%20one%20of%20the%20few%20Muslim-majority%20areas%20in%20the%20state%2C%20but%20has%20never%20faced%20rioting%20along%20communal%20lines.%20During%20the%20two-day%20violence%2C%20the%20local%20Muslim%20traders%20have%20suffered%20the%20biggest%20losses%20of%20property.%20They%20feel%20they%20were%20specifically%20stigmatised%20as%20cow%20traffickers%20first%20and%20then%20their%20businesses%20were%20targeted%20and%20destroyed.%20Many%20of%20them%20who%20could%20have%20simply%20locked%20up%20their%20homes%20and%20left%20for%20safer%20places.%20The%20migrant%20daily%20wagers%20in%20the%20area%20who%20have%20been%20doing%20construction%20work%2C%20whose%20wives%20were%20doing%20domestic%20work%20in%20the%20rich%20gated%20community%20homes%2C%20have%20neither%20money%20nor%20the%20means%20to%20flee.%20The%20housing%20societies%20have%20simply%20barred%20their%20entry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20ample%20proof%20that%20the%20heavily%20armed%20rampaging%20members%20of%20the%20Shobha%20Yatra%20targeted%20primarily%20Muslim%20businesses%20(meat%20and%20scrap)%20and%20looted%20and%20burnt%20shops%20owned%20by%20marginal%20Muslim%20traders.%20They%20also%20attacked%20and%20burnt%20two%20mosques%2C%20killed%20a%2019-year-old%20deputy%20imam%2C%20and%20have%20asked%20some%20500%20slum%20dwellers%20in%20the%20area%2C%20who%20they%20have%20decided%20are%20Bangladeshis%2C%20to%20leave%20within%20a%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20day%20after%20the%20rioting%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20issued%20a%20statement%20that%20offered%20little%20comfort%20to%20the%20affected.%20He%20talked%20of%20a%20larger%20conspiracy%20behind%20the%20communal%20violence.%20The%20members%20of%20preordained%20Yatra%20by%20the%20Bajrang%20Dal%20and%20the%20police%2C%20he%20pointed%20out%2C%20were%20also%20targeted%20by%20stone%20pelters%20from%20the%20area.%20The%20losses%20will%20be%20assessed%20and%20the%20guilty%20will%20be%20punished%20severely%2C%20he%20said%20solemnly.%20They%20will%20be%20made%20to%20pay%20for%20the%20losses.%20He%20also%20added%20that%20the%20police%20forces%20at%20his%20disposal%20were%20inadequate%20to%20maintain%20law%20and%20order%20for%20a%20population%20of%202.5%20crore.%20People%20must%20also%20guard%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20evening%20talk%20shows%2C%20The%20Virus%20dominated.%20When%20apportioning%20culpability%2C%20one%20saw%20the%20supporters%20of%20the%20ruling%20group%20hinting%20at%20usual%20qualifiers%20like%20%E2%80%98meat%20traders%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98cattle%20hustlers%E2%80%99%20or%20%E2%80%98links%20with%20BangladeshPakKashmir%E2%80%99%20to%20underscore%20the%20danger%20%E2%80%98they%E2%80%99%20posed%20to%20a%20prosperous%20and%20onward%20marching%20state%20like%20Haryana%20and%20its%20capital%20Gurugram.%20Gurugram%20has%20been%20showcased%20like%20a%20Bengaluru%20of%20the%20north%3A%20rich%2C%20progressive%2C%20replete%20with%20growth%20possibilities%20for%20Big%20Industry%2C%20abustle%20with%20building%20activity.%20It%20boasts%20of%20many%20posh%20high-rise%20buildings%20where%20the%20rich%20and%20modern%20citizens%20of%20India%20live.%20To%20those%20afflicted%20with%20the%20virus%20within%20such%20interconnected%20communities%2C%20the%20petty%20traders%20and%20scrap%20dealers%20and%20daily-wage%20labourers%20in%20Nuh%20are%20just%20people%20from%20the%20%3Cem%3Ebasti%3C%2Fem%3E%20who%20live%20in%20cramped%20ghettos%20surrounded%20by%20filth%2C%20drink%20dirty%20water%20and%20die%20young%20of%20various%20diseases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20why%20one%20senses%20a%20fear%20among%20India%E2%80%99s%20super%20rich%20%E2%80%93%20a%20fear%20of%20real%20change.%20If%20The%20Virus%20were%20ever%20to%20fade%20or%20leave%20India%2C%20the%20whole%20edifice%20of%20a%20hierarchical%20India%20could%20fade.%20Many%20things%20would%20no%20longer%20be%20deemed%20normal.%20It%20would%20be%20politically%20incorrect%20if%20the%20G-20%20were%20preceded%20and%20a%20Chandra%20Yan%20launch%20followed%20by%20communal%20riots.%20Insistence%20on%20making%20Hindi%20the%20%3Cem%3Erashtra%20bhasha%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20the%20medium%20of%20instruction%20in%20IITs%20and%20IIMs%2C%20while%20ministers%20and%20MPs%20send%20their%20own%20children%20to%20study%20abroad%20in%20Ivy%20League%20universities%2C%20would%20become%20almost%20unforgivable.%20Children%20from%20the%20ghettoised%20communities%20would%20stop%20distributing%20drugs%20to%20kids%20of%20the%20rich%20at%20their%20rave%20parties.%20Drunk%20brats%20of%20rich%20builders%20would%20not%20be%20able%20to%20get%20away%20after%20ramming%20their%20fancy%20cars%20into%20two%20wheelers%20or%20three%20wheelers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnless%20India%20acquires%20herd%20immunity%2C%20which%20seems%20unlikely%20so%20far%2C%20there%20are%20so%20many%20seams%20along%20which%20the%20virus%20of%20contempt%20will%20continue%20to%20rip%20apart%20communities%2C%20states%20and%20our%20democratic%20institutions.%C2%A0So%20the%20crucial%20question%20to%20all%20those%20preaching%20peace%20on%20earth%20and%20goodwill%20to%20all%20men%2C%20is%3A%20is%20there%20a%20real%20desire%20within%20this%20India%20to%20kill%20this%20virus%20and%20create%20a%20new%20India%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMrinal%20Pande%20is%20a%20writer%20and%20veteran%20journalist.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691312441000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F02105455%2F6.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fthe-age-of-contempt%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Contempt%20is%20deadlier%20than%20simple%20hate.%20Hate%20has%20a%20target%20and%20a%20vendetta-driven%20agenda%20that%20it%20follows%20with%20cunning%2C%20keeping%20itself%20hidden.%20One%20carrying%20the%20virus%20of%20contempt%20does%20not%20care.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fthe-age-of-contempt%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Jamie%20Foxx%20apologises%20and%20deletes%20Instagram%20post%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691312250000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2FADD0%2Fproduction%2F_130669444_gettyimages-1466518646.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fentertainment-arts-66420841%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20actor%20says%20he%20never%20intended%20to%20cause%20offence%20after%20his%20post%20was%20accused%20of%20being%20antisemitic.%22%2C%2