embassy-russia-criticises-treatment-citizens-border-2023-08-05%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EReuters%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20report%20regarding%20the%20statement%2C%20the%20five%20Chinese%20citizens%20were%20trying%20to%20enter%20Russia%20via%20Kazakhstan%20late%20last%20month.%20They%20were%20not%20allowed%20to%20enter%20after%20four%20hours%20of%20questioning%20and%20their%20visas%20were%20cancelled%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20report%20said%20that%20the%20Chinese%20embassy%20officials%20%E2%80%9Cmade%20representation%E2%80%9D%20to%20Russia%E2%80%99s%20Foreign%20Ministry%2C%20Federal%20Security%20Bureau%20and%20Federal%20Border%20Guard%20Service%20after%20a%20video%20of%20the%20incident%20surfaced.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20goes%20against%20the%20big%20picture%20of%20Sino-Russian%20friendship%20and%20the%20growing%20trend%20of%20friendly%20people-to-people%20exchanges%20between%20the%20two%20countries%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBloomberg%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Equoted%20the%20Chinese%20statement%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20standoff%20comes%20after%20Russian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20and%20Chinese%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20had%20last%20year%20proclaimed%20that%20there%20were%20%E2%80%9Cno%20limits%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20friendship%20between%20the%20two%20countries.%20China%20has%20refused%20to%20condemn%20Russia%E2%80%99s%20war%20against%20Ukraine%20and%20the%20bilateral%20relations%20the%20countries%20have%20not%20seen%20a%20change.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20now%2C%20China%20has%20demanded%20answers%20from%20Russia%20on%20this%20incident.%20The%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20report%20about%20the%20Chinese%20statement%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20language%20used%20in%20the%20Chinese%20embassy%E2%