%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20toys%20look%20like%20us%20and%20are%20dressed%20in%20traditional%20clothes%2C%20like%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F95506%2Fhironmoy-gogoi-assamese-ethnic-food%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eauthentic%20Assamese%20%3C%2Fa%3Esaree%2C%20along%20with%20traditional%20accessories%2C%20swords%20etc.%20The%20attire%20can%20be%20changed.%20All%20the%20toys%20are%20handmade%20and%20plastic%20free.%20We%20also%20make%20soft%20toys%20of%20animals%20such%20as%20wild%20buffalo%20and%20fish%2C%20as%20they%20have%20a%20great%20significance%20to%20the%20people%20of%20the%20community%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHandmade%2C%20plastic-free%20toys%20that%20tell%20stories%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKirat%20says%20that%20all%20the%20materials%20used%20to%20create%20these%20toys%20are%20sourced%20from%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F302408%2Fhistory-of-ima-keithal-largest-all-women-market-imphal-manipur-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20local%20markets.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20local%20economy%20needs%20a%20good%20boost%3B%20my%20community%E2%80%99s%20youth%20do%20not%20have%20many%20opportunities.%20They%20either%20leave%20the%20village%20and%20move%20to%20cities%20or%20join%20the%20Army.%20I%20try%20to%20employ%20as%20many%20artisans%20from%20the%20community%20itself%20to%20provide%20them%20with%20a%20work%20opportunity%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20says%20they%20have%20sold%20around%20100%20toys%20so%20far.%20Each%20toy%20is%20usually%20priced%20anywhere%20between%20Rs%20800%20to%20Rs%203%2C000%20depending%20on%20the%20work%20involved.%20They%20are%20also%20working%20on%20adding%20more%20categories.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20people%20receive%20our%20toys%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20love%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20rema