%20feel%20how%20a%20citizen%20should%20feel%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%2053-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMulti-level%20approach%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20pursuing%20their%20higher%20education%20at%20Azim%20Premji%20University%20and%20doing%20internships%2C%20they%20observed%20the%20dire%20educational%20state%20of%20migrant%20children.%20To%20address%20these%20gaps%20in%20educational%20exclusion%2C%20Gubbachi%20mainstreams%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F241795%2Fbengaluru-sub-inspector-teaches-migrant-labourers-students-classes-free-education-police-san196%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emigrant%20children%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethrough%20various%20age-appropriate%20programmes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENomita%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20enrol%20children%20aged%206-9%20in%20a%20bridge%20learning%20program.%20Our%20fast-track%20curriculum%20covers%20a%20two-year%20course%20in%20just%20one%20year.%20We%20teach%20the%20subjects%20in%20their%20native%20language%20to%20strengthen%20their%20understanding%20and%20also%20help%20them%20with%20the%20regional%20language%20used%20in%20the%20school%20they%20want%20to%20join.%20The%20training%20lasts%20for%20one%20or%20two%20years.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20children%20are%20bridged%20to%20their%20learning%20levels%2C%20they%20are%20mainstreamed%20in%20a%20government%20school.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20after%20enrolling%20them%20in%20schools%2C%20we%20found%20that%20there%20are%20hardly%20enough%20teachers%20to%20manage%20hundreds%20of%20students.%20It%20was%20impractical%20for%20us%20to%20expect%20any%20kind%20of%20learning%20for%20our%20children.%20The%20students%20complained%20to%20us%20that%20nothing%20was%20being%20taught%20in%20schools.%20Having%20worked%20so%20hard%20to%20mainstream%20them%2C%20if%20they%20dropped%20out%2C%20then%20all%20efforts%20would%20go%20to%20waste%2C%E2%80%9D%20co-founder%20Manimakalai%20tell