ejected%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20now%2018-year-old%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20he%20learnt%20about%20Gubbachi%20from%20his%20father%E2%80%99s%20employer.%20The%20same%20year%2C%20he%20joined%20the%20non-profit%E2%80%99s%20programme%2C%20where%20he%20was%20trained%20to%20read%20and%20write%20English%20and%20understand%20Mathematics.%20After%20a%20year%2C%20the%20organisation%20helped%20him%20enrol%20for%20senior%20secondary%20schooling%20(Class%2010)%20at%20the%20National%20Institute%20of%20Open%20Schooling%20(NIOS)%2C%20a%20government-run%20%E2%80%9Copen%20school%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20explained%20concepts%20to%20me%20in%20my%20language%20and%20helped%20me%20read%20textbooks.%20They%20emphasised%20that%20memorising%20exact%20vocabulary%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20necessary%2C%20and%20I%20always%20wrote%20down%20what%20I%20understood.%20This%20approach%20made%20it%20easier%20for%20me%20to%20grasp%20the%20subjects%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fb44aafaa-d724-4fd0-af5d-359b0b5607d1-1690981573.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Gubbachi%20mainstreams%20migrant%20children%20through%20various%20age-appropriate%20programmes.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fb44aafaa-d724-4fd0-af5d-359b0b5607d1-1690981573.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fb44aafaa-d724-4fd0-af5d-359b0b5607d1-1690981573-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fb44aafaa-d724-4fd0-af5d-359b0b5607d1-1690981573-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fb44aafaa-d724-4fd0-af5d-359b0b5607d1-1690981573-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fb44aafaa-d724-4fd0-af5d-359b0b5607d1-1690981573-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-326098%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EGubbachi%20mainstreams%20migrant%20children%20through%20various%20age-appropriate%20programmes.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20getting%20hold%20of%20the%20basics%2C%20Vijay%20appeared%20for%20the%20Class%2010%20examination%20and%20secured%2088.5%20percent%20in%202021.%20Subsequently%2C%20he%20completed%20his%20Class%2012%20with%2072%20percent.%20Not%20only%20this%2C%20he%20even%20got%20a%20chance%20to%20join%20Azim%20Premji%20University%20on%20a%20full%20scholarship%20for%20the%20entire%20course.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20because%20of%20Gubbachi%20that%20I%20was%20able%20to%20get%20an%20education%20and%20study%2C%20first%20in%20a%20convent%20school%2C%20and%20then%20in%20a%20university.%20This%20achievement%20has%20transformed%20me%20a%20lot.%20I%20learnt%20why%20education%20is%20important%20and%20how%20it%20helps%20in%20life.%20My%20parents%20are%20proud%20that%20I%20am%20continuing%20my%20education%20because%20they%20never%20got%20the%20chance%20to%20study%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilar%20to%20Vijay%2C%20the%20non-profit%20has%20assisted%20more%20than%204%2C000%20migrant%20children%20from%20states%20like%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Bihar%2C%20Assam%2C%20Odisha%2C%20and%20West%20Bengal%20in%20joining%20mainstream%20schools%20without%20any%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20handhold%20them%20right%20from%20their%20schooling%20to%20college%20enrollment.%20Our%20dream%20is%20to%20see%20all%20children%2C%20like%20Vijay%2C%20get%20into%20good%20universities.%20When%20impoverished%20families%20move%20to%20new%20states%2C%20we%20want%20them%20to%20feel%20secure%20and%20cared%20for.%20Every%20child%20deserves