he%20long%20travel%20times%20and%20waiting%20periods%20of%20five%20to%20six%20hours%20for%20a%20short%20consultation%20lead%20many%20women%20to%20avoid%20these%20visits%20and%20postpone%20them%20to%20the%20next%20month.%20However%2C%20this%20delay%20prevents%20potential%20risks%20from%20being%20assessed%20in%20a%20timely%20manner.%20I%20became%20aware%20of%20the%20alarming%20mortality%20rates%20among%20tribal%20and%20rural%20pregnant%20women%20and%20felt%20determined%20to%20find%20a%20solution%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20after%20creating%20a%20simple%20device%20for%20his%20sister%2C%20Senthil%20felt%20inspired%20to%20assist%20more%20women%2C%20particularly%20those%20in%20rural%20and%20remote%20areas.%20His%20aim%20was%20to%20help%20them%20monitor%20essential%20vitals%20usually%20recorded%20during%20antenatal%20visits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20three%20years%20of%20clinical%20trials%2C%20he%20founded%20JioVio%20Healthcare%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMonitoring%20vitals%20in%20a%20single%20device%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20the%20process%20of%20reaching%20out%20to%20rural%20women%2C%20Senthil%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20work%20with%20the%20state%20governments.%20After%20contacting%20them%2C%20the%20secretaries%20inform%20us%20about%20the%20districts%20with%20high%20maternal%20mortality.%20We%20then%20approach%20the%20district%20collector%2C%20who%20onboards%20block-level%20officers%2C%20healthcare%20workers%2C%20and%20rural%20women.%20When%20any%20of%20the%20rural%20women%20get%20pregnant%2C%20a%20mobile%20application%20is%20used%20to%20track%20their%20health%20and%20conduct%20monthly%20checkups.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fjiovio-1-1690550129.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C