pressure%2C%20doctors%20also%20consider%20her%20sleep%20pattern.%20If%20she%20isn%E2%80%99t%20getting%20proper%20sleep%2C%20it%20can%20contribute%20to%20increased%20blood%20pressure.%20In%20such%20cases%2C%20the%20doctor%20may%20prescribe%20different%20medications%20instead%20of%20a%20standard%20blood%20pressure%20tablet.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20data%20is%20collected%20weekly%20and%20reviewed%20by%20a%20doctor%20every%2015%20days.%20High-risk%20mothers%20are%20recommended%20to%20use%20the%20wearable%20device%20for%201%2C000%20days%20%E2%80%94%20starting%20from%20the%20fourth%20week%20of%20pregnancy%20until%20the%20baby%E2%80%99s%20second%20birthday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fjiovio-1690549999.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Senthil%20also%20created%20a%20smart%20wearable%20device%20called%20Allowear%2C%20designed%20for%20high-risk%20pregnant%20women%20who%20need%20continuous%20monitoring.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fjiovio-1690549999.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fjiovio-1690549999-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fjiovio-1690549999-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fjiovio-1690549999-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fjiovio-1690549999-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-325671%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESenthil%20also%20created%20a%20smart%20wearable%20device%20called%20Allowear%2C%20designed%20for%20high-risk%20pregnant%20women%20who%20need%20continuous%20monitoring.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cost%20for%20this%20service%20is%20only%20Re%201%20per%20day%2C%20covered%20by%20the%20government.%20Senthil%20says%20that%20their%20annual%20revenue%20is%20about%20Rs%201.5%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECommenting%20on%20how%20useful%20the%20devices%20are%2C%20Madurai-based%20Dr%20S%20Karthikeyan%2C%20who%20has%20been%20practising%20medicine%20for%2013%20years%2C%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20seen%20that%20a%20lot%20of%20pregnant%20women%20do%20not%20take%20care%20of%20themselves%20which%20causes%20nutritional%20deficiencies%20among%20them.%20This%20changes%20their%20blood%20glucose%20and%20pressure%2C%20and%20ECG.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWith%20these%20devices%2C%20we%20are%20able%20to%20understand%20the%20problems%20and%20alert%20local%20healthcare%20workers.%20Accordingly%2C%20we%20are%20also%20able%20to%20prescribe%20iron%20supplements%2C%20folic%20acid%20tablets%2C%20and%20other%20nutrition%20supplements%20to%20the%20women.%20I%20can%20monitor%20their%20health%20by%20sitting%20in%20my%20OPD.%20We%20have%20been%20able%20to%20save%20hundreds%20of%20lives%20thanks%20to%20these%20devices.%20They%20have%20a%20huge%20potential%20to%20reduce%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F175789%2Fias-hero-telangana-maternal-mortality-un-sdg-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ematernal%20mortality%20%3C%2Fa%3Erate%20in%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenthil%20claims%20that%20he%20has%20been%20able%20to%20reduce%20maternal%20mortality%20by%2010%20percent%20in%20the%20regions%20he%20has%20worked.%20For%20him%2C%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20work%20is%20extremely%20satisfying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20five%20years%20into%20any%20corporate%20job%2C%20the%20work%20is%20pretty%20much%20the%20same.%20I%20chose%20entrepreneurship%20because%20it%20gives%20me%20more%20learning%20opportunities.%20Instead%20of%20working%20in%20a%20big%20Fortune%20500%20company%2C%20this%20work%20gives%20me%20immense%20gratification.%20It%20is%20fulfilling%20to%20see%20we%20are%20able%20to%20save%20lives%20with%20our%20devices%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenthil%20shares%20that%20he%20now%20intends%20to%20expand%20their%20services%20in%20North%20and%20Northeast%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESource%3A%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Frchiips.org%2Fnfhs%2FNFHS-5_FCTS%2FIndia.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ENational%20Family%20Health%20Survey%20%E2%80%93%205%3A%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3EPublished%20by%20Ministry%20of%20Health%20and%20Family%20Welfare.%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FFeaturesDeatils.aspx%3FNoteId%3D151238%26ModuleId%2520%3D%25202%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESignificant%20Decline%20in%20Maternal%20Mortality%20in%20India%3A%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3EPublished%20by%20Press%20Information%20Bureau%20on%2014%20December%202022.%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat.%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EAll%20photos%3A%20Senthil%20Kumar%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690809914000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fjiovio-2-1690550162.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D325599%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Madurai%E2%80%99s%20Senthil%20Kumar%20started%20JioVio%20Healthcare%2C%20which%20provides%20early%20risk%20monitoring%20for%20pregnant%20women%20in%20rural%20India.%20So%20far%2C%20he%20has%20catered%20to%2030%20lakh%20women%20in%20Kerala%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20Karnataka%2C%20and%20Tamil%20Nadu.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A31%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F325599%2Fmadurai-jiovio-healthcare-startup-pregnancy-risk-monitoring-device-rural-women-infant-mortality%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20We%20Know%20So%20Little%20About%20The%20U.S.%20%E2%80%98Union-Busting%E2%80%99%20Industry%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22Weak%20disclosure%20rules%20have%20helped%20keep%20anti-union%20consulting%20and%20legal%20work%20in%20the%20shadows.%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690551969000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fimg.huffingtonpost.com%2Fasset%2F64c291632400001900572ade.jpg%3Fcache%3Dueakpq0a9b%26ops%3D224_126%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentry%2Fwhy-we-know-so-little-about-the-us-union-busting-industry_n_64c28622e4b03ad2b897077f%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Weak%20disclosure%20rules%20have%20helped%20keep%20anti-union%20consulting%20and%20legal%20work%20in%20the%20shadows.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A235%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentry%2Fwhy-we-know-so-little-about-the-us-union-busting-industry_n_64c28622e4b03ad2b897077f%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Do%20Brands%20Manage%20Plastic%20Waste%3F%20Entrepreneur%E2%80%99s%20Credits%20System%20Cuts%2045000%20KG%20From%20Landfills%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDo%20you%20remember%20how%20you%20spent%20your%20free%20time%20in%20Class%2012%3F%20Most%20of%20us%20spent%20it%20playing%20sports%20like%20football%2C%20cricket%2C%20or%20badminton%2C%20whereas%20some%20dedicated%20students%20used%20that%20time%20to%20study%20for%20the%20board%20exams.%20But%20not%20Bhagyashree%20Bhansali.%20She%20went%20and%20joined%20the%202011%20anti-corruption%20movement%20launched%20by%20activist%20Anna%20Hazare.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20devoted%20her%20college%20life%20to%20addressing%20public%20grievances.%20While%20pursuing%20her%20bachelor%E2%80%99s%20in%20business%20administration%2C%20she%20joined%20the%20Delhi%20government%E2%80%99s%20advisory%20team.%20She%20focused%20on%20environmental%20issues%20such%20as%20air%20and%20water%20pollution%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F323755%2Fmothers-anupama-charulatha-swmrt-bengaluru-plastic-free-low-waste-wedding-composting%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emunicipal%20waste%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20biodiversity%20loss%2C%20which%20have%20been%20persistent%20challenges%20for%20the%20capital%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20work%20involved%20thinking%20of%20different%20ways%20to%20manage%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20waste%2C%20which%20led%20her%20to%20the%20Ghazipur%20landfill%2C%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20garbage%20dump%20yards%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20that%20time%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20were%20facing%20health%20issues%20due%20to%20environmental%20pollution.%20We%20would%20make%20multiple%20visits%20to%20the%20Ghazipur%20landfill%20and%20seeing%20its%20condition%20just%20shook%20me.%20I%20was%20frustrated%20seeing%20the%20sheer%20number%20of%20plastic%20bottles%20and%20chip%20packets%20there%3B%20the%20amount%20of%20plastic%20waste%20there%20was%20humongous%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bhagyashree%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20published%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20Ghazipur%20landfill%20has%2078%20lakh%20MT%20of%20waste%20and%20reached%20its%20saturation%20point%20in%202002.%20Yet%2C%20700%20MT%20of%20waste%20is%20dumped%20there%20daily.%20Work%20is%20underway%20by%20the%20Municipal%20Corporation%20of%20Delhi%20(MCD)%20to%20flatten%20the%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMaking%20recycling%20her%20life%20mission%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201328px)%20100vw%2C%201328px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftdc-11-min-1690546328.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221328%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Trash%20being%20separated%20in%20a%20dumpyard%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftdc-11-min-1690546328.jpeg%201328w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftdc-11-min-1690546328-300x168.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftdc-11-min-1690546328-500x280.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftdc-11-min-1690546328-768x431.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftdc-11-min-1690546328-150x84.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-325579%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22745%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ETrash%20being%20separated%20in%20a%20dumpyard%20by%20TDC%E2%80%99s%20workers%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhagyashree%20interacted%20with%20rag%20pickers%20and%20waste%20segregators%20to%20understand%20what%20happens%20to%20plastic%20waste.%20%E2%80%9CBack%20then%2C%20most%20of%20the%20waste%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20recycled%3B%20it%20was%20just%20incinerated%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%20adding%20that%20she%20was%20determined%20to%20be%20part%20of%20the%20solution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20weren%E2%80%99t%20a%20lot%20of%20recycling%20units%20then.%20While%20looking%20at%20options%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20plastic%20menace%2C%20I%20met%20someone%20who%20wanted%20to%20establish%20a%20recycling%20unit%20in%20Delhi.%20So%20I%20helped%20him%20set%20up%20the%20unit.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20during%20the%20process%20of%20setting%20up%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F319912%2Ftamil-nadu-father-son-duo-senthil-kumar-recycle-plastic-bottles-into-sustainable-clothes%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecycling%20unit%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethat%20Bhagyashree%20learnt%20a%20lot%20about%20plastic%20recycling.%20She%20went%20to%20various%20exhibitions%20to%20see%20the%20different%20recycling%20machines%20used%20across%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMachines%20used%20in%20Germany%20and%20China%20would%20segregate%20the%20waste%2C%20but%20those%20machines%20could%20not%20process%20the%20type%20of%20waste%20we%20produced.%20So%20we%20had%20to%20segregate%20and%20clean%20the%20waste%20properly%20before%20using%20the%20machines%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%2029-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20they%20set%20up%20small%20segregation%20systems%20and%20tweaked%20the%20machinery%20to%20work%20according%20to%20the%20waste%20they%20needed%20to%20recycle%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20college%2C%20she%20continued%20to%20work%20with%20local%20recyclers%20and%20partnered%20with%20organisations%20like%20Mohan%20Meakins%2C%20Whirlpool%2C%20and%20Arvind%20Mills%20to%20establish%20efficient%20in-house%20plastic%20waste%20management%20systems.%20%E2%80%9CI%20learnt%20how%20to%20identify%20different%20kinds%20of%20plastic%2C%20its%20nature%2C%20qualities%20and%20recyclability%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20these%20learnings%20which%20eventually%20led%20to%20her%20startup%2C%20The%20Disposal%20Company%20(TDC).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ELove%20for%20skincare%20turned%20into%20a%20business%20idea%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201113px)%20100vw%2C%201113px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftdc-7-1690546256.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221113%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Plastic%20waste%20being%20processed%20by%20TDC%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftdc-7-1690546256.jpeg%201113w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftdc-7-1690546256-300x192.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftdc-7-1690546256-500x320.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftdc-7-1690546256-768x491.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftdc-7-1690546256-150x96.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-325576%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22712%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EPlastic%20waste%20is%20recycled%20by%20TDC%20in%20partnership%20with%20recyclers%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20February%202020%2C%20Bhagyashree%20moved%20to%20Rajasthan%20after%20getting%20married.%20In%20Jaipur%2C%20she%20again%20started%20consulting%20with%20the%20government%20on%20ways%20to%20manage%20waste%20better.%20But%20a%20month%20later%2C%20the%20nation%20went%20under%20lockdown.%20COVID%20also%20made%20it%20harder%20to%20deal%20with%20waste%2C%20says%20the%20entrepreneur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20worked%20with%20the%20local%20pollution%20control%20board%20during%20the%20lockdown.%20With%20the%20addition%20of%20used%20masks%20and%20gloves%2C%20we%20had%20to%20figure%20out%20ways%20to%20segregate%20contaminated%20waste%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20pandemic%20also%20saw%20a%20rise%20in%20D2C%20(direct-to-consumer)%20brands%2C%20including%20skincare.%20Newly%20married%2C%20she%20says%20she%20loved%20trying%20on%20different%20skincare%20products.%20But%20while%20others%20focussed%20on%20the%20product%2C%20Bhagyashree%20focused%20on%20the%20packaging!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEvery%20time%20I%20see%20a%20new%20brand%2C%20the%20first%20thing%20that%20catches%20my%20eye%20is%20the%20packaging.%20Almost%20100%20new%20brands%20have%20come%20up%2C%20and%20most%20FMCG%20(fast-moving%20consumer%20goods)%20brands%20use%20low-value%20packaging.%20I%20was%20horrified%20at%20the%20waste%20we%20are%20accumulating%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20now%20Mumbai-based%20businesswoman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F311038%2Fmani-vajipey-raj-madangopal-banyan-nation-hyderabad-recycle-plastic-waste-into-fmcg-bottles-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplastic%20waste%3C%2Fa%3E%20generated%20by%20so%20many%20new%20brands%20with%20new%20types%20of%20packaging%20gave%20her%20sleepless%20nights.%20This%20led%20her%20to%20start%20The%20Disposal%20Company%20in%20November%202020%20to%20%E2%80%9Creduce%20waste%2C%20revive%20lives%20and%20restore%20the%20ecological%20balance.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20startup%20is%20a%20plastic%20credit%20platform%20that%20helps%20brands%20neutralise%20their%20plastic%20waste.%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCqdA8n1ISWi%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCqdA8n1ISWi%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCqdA8n1ISWi%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20The%20Disposal%20Company%20(%40thedisposalcompany)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20claims%20that%20it%20is%20one%20of%20the%20first%20startups%20to%20do%20this%20in%20India%2C%20which%20gave%20them%20the%20first-mover%20advantage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Disposal%20Company%20neutralises%20the%20plastic%20waste%20generated%20by%20a%20brand%20by%20recovering%20an%20equal%20amount%20of%20plastic%20from%20landfills%20and%20recycling%20it.%20We%20then%20report%20it%20to%20the%20Central%20Pollution%20Control%20Board%20(CPCB)%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20the%20process%2C%20Bhagyashree%20says%20they%20first%20educate%20brands%20on%20how%20to%20improve%20their%20packaging%20and%20eliminate%20plastic%20wherever%20possible.%20They%20work%20with%20design%20labs%20to%20do%20so.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20ideal%20thing%20is%20to%20reduce%20plastic.%20In%20some%20cases%2C%20brands%20can%E2%80%99t%20afford%20to%2C%20or%20their%20products%20can%E2%80%99t%20sustain%20in%20other%20forms%20of%20packaging.%20In%20those%20cases%2C%20we%20help%20them%20reduce%20their%20footprint%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETDC%20works%20with%2070%20brands%20across%20India%2C%20Singapore%20and%20the%20UK.%20Its%20clients%20include%20companies%20like%20mCaffeine%2C%20Slurrp%20Farm%2C%20The%20Souled%20Store%2C%20Bombay%20Shaving%20Company%2C%20Blue%20Tokai%20Coffee%2C%20and%20SLAY%20Coffee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20collaborates%20with%20rag%20pickers%20and%20waste%20segregators%20to%20retrieve%20plastic%20waste.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20provide%20training%20and%20support%20to%20improve%20waste%20workers%E2%80%99%20skills.%20We%20also%20give%20them%20proper%20safety%20gear.%20We%20have%20provided%20jobs%20to%20500%20such%20waste%20workers%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Bhagyashree.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20TDC%20knows%20the%20amount%20of%20plastic%20waste%20that%20needs%20to%20be%20neutralised%2C%20they%20retrieve%20that%20much%20waste%20from%20the%20Ghazipur%20landfills%20with%20the%20help%20of%20rag%20pickers.%20Once%20retrieved%2C%20they%20segregate%20the%20plastic%20and%20send%20it%20to%20recyclers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETDC%20works%20with%20recycling%20companies%20like%20Thermowaste%20Solutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20recycle%20plastic%20waste%20into%20granules.%20We%20sell%20these%20granules%20to%20companies%20who%20use%20them%20to%20make%20sustainable%20products%20like%20photo%20frames%2C%20toys%20etc.%20Mixed%20plastic%2C%20which%20we%20can%E2%80%99t%20recycle%2C%20is%20sent%20to%20a%20plant%20that%20converts%20it%20to%20energy.%20We%20recycle%20about%2060%20metric%20tonnes%20of%20waste%20per%20month.%2020%E2%80%9325%20metric%20tonnes%20of%20credit%20is%20given%20to%20TDC%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Sanyam%20Jain%20of%20Thermowaste%20Solutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECreating%20a%20better%20planet%20for%20the%20future%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201196px)%20100vw%2C%201196px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftdc-14-min-1690546327.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221196%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Waste%20being%20picked%20up%20by%20TDC%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftdc-14-min-1690546327.jpeg%201196w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftdc-14-min-1690546327-300x167.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftdc-14-min-1690546327-500x278.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftdc-14-min-1690546327-768x427.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.theb