rney%20to%20acknowledge%20how%20far%20they%20have%20come%2C%20the%20odds%20they%20have%20traversed%2C%20and%20how%20we%20may%20mobilise%20the%20community%2C%20garner%20support%2C%20and%20instil%20belief.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EIt%20is%20important%20to%20remember%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20a%20%E2%80%98one%20size%20fits%20all%E2%80%99%20phenomenon.%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20as%20one%E2%80%99s%20experience%20with%20disability%20is%20subjective%2C%20so%20is%20their%20understanding%20of%20Disability%20Pride%20%E2%80%94%20it%E2%80%99s%20all%20about%20your%20lived%20experience.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20a%20young%20adult%2C%20%E2%80%98Disability%20Pride%E2%80%99%20seemed%20inauthentic%20and%20more%20of%20a%20propaganda%20campaign.%20I%20have%20faced%20so%20many%20challenges%20and%20lived%20so%20many%20awkward%20moments%20as%20a%20person%20with%20a%20locomotor%20disability.%20How%20could%20I%20be%20proud%20of%20my%20disability%3F%20But%20as%20I%20grew%20older%2C%20I%20realised%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20about%20understanding%20what%20our%20disability%20is%20to%20us%2C%20being%20comfortable%20in%20our%20own%20skin%20and%20celebrating%20our%20journey%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Kavya%2C%20a%20job%20coach%20at%20v-shesh%2C%20an%20enterprise%20that%20prepares%20organisations%20with%20disability%20inclusion.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Anjali%20Vyas%2C%20who%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F317421%2Fhow-to-build-inclusive-workplace-navigate-blood-disorders-thalassemia-with-employers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elives%20with%20an%20invisible%20disability%3C%2Fa%3E%20called%20Multiple%20Sclerosis%2C%20%E2%80%9CDisability%20Pride%20has%20no%20visible%20boundaries.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22h